18.18: Daa-witq tau sau-lo, “yem i-saa-laa-en kua'q yia tovb haiq taub? yia Eei Zyenb Ze'q fai yia Eei tia Eei trub zov yaag tovb haiq taub? yia fuvg haib Pwij tu'q zruj huvb tiaj Eei sia'g laavb?”
18.8: sau-lo za'kevb! Qiaj Jiad haig. naaiq teij waag maiq hxpg ninb Eei Hruq. ninb kxvq, “ninb Bua Zev Daa-witq taij myenb penj waanb waang, mq paag ninb Bua kxvq yia taij myenb penj Zinb Zin Navq. Zwrtq liud kua'q zavg Daa-witq cvj haib tu'q haiq Euvg?”
18.3: yo-naa-Taan zyrug Zauj Daa-witq lcvd Jiad vcvg waag, weig zu'g ninb Namq Daa-witq Dovg Namq ninb kanb Eei mcvg.
18.21: sau-lo yem Hruq Namq, “yia puvj yia Eei sia'q pun ninb weig pun yia Eei sia'q Navq Laav Lopq Jyenq ninb, fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei puad zyrug haib hxig ninb a'q.” Navq naaig, sau-lo zyrug kxvq ta'Eeig Rung Buaj Daa-witq, “meib xij zu'g zruj yia Eei sia'g laavb.”
18.14: maiq kunq Daa-witq zruj haiq Euvg ninb yaag zruj tu'q Zwrtq Eei, weig zu'g zyruq Zauj ninb yem.
18.23: sau-lo Eei pru zyrug zx'q naaiq teij waag kxvq pun Daa-witq mwavj, mq paag Daa-witq kxvq “meib Bua laaig zruj huvb tiaj Eei sia'g laavb se faib fiuq Eei sig fai? yia penj myenb Jomg myenb, maiq maaib haiq Euvg mevb hog Eei myenb.”
18.6: Daa-witq taij liud uaq taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb, Zauj Jyenq zwavj myenb Rwrnj uaq zang, maaib teij msia'q txn yem i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj zivb Zwrtq taaib Zavj heij paauj Jyenq Ruv taaib zipq sau-lo huvb. ninb Bua Fyenb yrub Eei paauj Ruv Bx'q lxb Bx'q Rod yaag Patq taanb paab.
18.2: uaq Nxi sau-lo lyrub Jyenq Daa-witq Zauj ninb yem, maiq pun Rwrnj ninb Eei tia Eei pyauq.
18.20: sau-lo Eei kanb taub sia'q, mi-Kaan, Namq Daa-witq. maaib myenb mivb Buaj sau-lo. sau-lo yaag hxpg Hruq Eei.
18.24: sau-lo Eei pru Buaj sau-lo, “Daa-witq Navq naaiq kxvq.”
18.28: sau-lo mavg yaag hiuq tu'q zyruq Zauj Daa-witq yem. sau-lo Eei sia'q mi-Kaan yaag Namq Daa-witq.
18.7: uaq teij msia'q txn yetg ping Zavj heij, yetg ping paauj Ruv, tau Jaaj kxvq, “sau-lo taij myenb penj Zinb Zin, Daa-witq taij myenb penj waanb waang.”
18.29: sau-lo zyrug kaub fatq kamb Riaj Daa-witq. Navq naaig sau-lo zanb zang zruj Daa-witq Eei winb wavq.
18.19: Ga'haaq Tauj zyavb hog puvj sau-lo Eei sia'q, me-laapq, Jiu pun Daa-witq, mq paag sau-lo puvj pun aatg-li-en myenb, me-hoj-laa, lovg zruj auq mig a'q.
18.17: sau-lo kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “naaiq se yia Eei sia'g Lo, Buaj heug me-laapq. yia xij pun meib lovg zruj auq. meib Kuvj xij zu'g weig yia zruj taamq Lo, Tevj zyruq Bx'q Jaaj.” weig zu'g sau-lo yem Hruq Namq, “yia maiq lovg yia Eei puad hxig ninb. yia pun fi-li-saa-tia myenb hxig ninb Navq.”
18.30: fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei pcvb pyeiq zanb zang Zwrtq taaib Bx'q Jaaj. maiq kunq ninb Bua Zwrtq taaib Bu'ziaj Rung, Daa-witq Bx'q hivb kaub Zamq sau-lo Eei zwavj pcvb pyeiq. Daa-witq zyrug tu'q mevb taub Lo haig.
18.27: Daa-witq Zauj kan ninb Eei myenb mivb taij Eig pc'q taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb. Daa-witq zyrug txb uaq teij myenb Eei yetg zuvq Jaib zweiq Dopq taaib zx'q pwavq sruj mrug pun huvb tiaj weig pun ninb tu'q zruj huvb tiaj Eei sia'g laavb. sau-lo zyrug zx'q ninb Eei sia'q mi-Kaan, puvj pun Daa-witq lovg zruj auq.
18.11: sau-lo zyrug piu Zav mivb. ninb yem Hruq Namq, “yia xij Ropq Daa-witq pavg Fovg tiv Jyenq.” mq paag i Rung Daa-witq zuvq simq Dutq mig a'q.
18.5: maiq kunq sau-lo Paaiq Daa-witq mivb zruj haiq Euvg, Daa-witq yaag zruj tu'q Zwrtq Eei. sau-lo zyrug xn Daa-witq zruj Junb pcv Eei pyeiq. Navq naaiq zruj, zwavj pc'g fivj Zauj sau-lo Eei Jyen yetg zuvq a'Neiq Eei.
18.9: yem uaq Nxi taaib sau-lo puvj mziv mavg Jyenq Daa-witq.
18.16: mq paag i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb Zauj yu-Daa myenb Namq Daa-witq, weig zu'g Daa-witq zanb zang txb ninb Bua pia'g pia'g Zwrtg Zwrtq.
18.4: yo-naa-Taan zyrug Jaiq ninb Eei lwib Daauq Zauj Bx'q Jaaj Eei lwi, lyemb ninb Eei Ru'g Daauq Zauj Jwavb zinj Zauj hrub Laav pun Daa-witq.
18.10: ta'Eeig Nxi maaib taub x'q Eei myenq yem Tinb huvb taaib mxb sau-lo. sau-lo yem kanb Eei pyauq Qa'q kxvq maiq Rav Eei waag. Daa-witq Navq yetg kau Patq taanb paab pun sau-lo mwavj. sau-lo Eei puad nanq Jyenq Zav.
18.22: sau-lo kxvq Buaj ninb Eei pru, “xij zu'g pivj Jyenq kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, ‘huvb tiaj a'Neiq haig meib. huvb tiaj Eei yetg zuvq pru yaag Namq meib. Navq naaig, meib kunq zruj huvb tiaj Eei sia'g laavb a'q.’+”
18.12: sau-lo zyrug kamb Riaj Daa-witq, weig zu'g zyruq Zauj Daa-witq yem mq paag leib Gxi sau-lo mig a'q.
18.15: sau-lo pwatg Daa-witq zruj tu'q Zwrtq Euvb Euvg ninb zyrug kamb Riaj haig Daa-witq.
18.13: Navq naaig sau-lo heug swiq Daa-witq mivb leib Gxi ninb, yaag xn ninb kunq yetg Zin taub pcv. Daa-witq txb pcv pia'g pia'g Zwrtg Zwrtq Eei Bx'q Jaaj.
18.1: Daa-witq Zauj sau-lo kxvq liud waag, yo-naa-Taan za'kevb Namq haig Daa-witq, zuvq Namq Dovg Namq ninb kanb Eei mcvg.
18.26: uaq teij pru zyrug kxvq naaiq teij waag pun Daa-witq mwavj. Daa-witq zyrug pwavq Hruq zruj huvb tiaj Eei sia'g laavb. tivg zyavj Eei zyavb hog maiq kcvb Tauj,
18.25: sau-lo kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “meib Bua kunq Navq naaiq kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, ‘huvb tiaj maiq lovg haiq Euvg leib kiv. Kuvj xij lovg fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei yetg pc'q nxm Jaib zweiq Dopq weig Jaauq syrub pun huvb tiaj Eei winb wavq.’+” sau-lo taaq za'eij pun fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei puad taij Daa-witq.

8.18: Tauj uaq Nxi meib Bua xij laaij meib Bua kanb kinq taaib Eei huvb tiaj zu'g Kruq, heug Jyenq Toq zyruq, mq paag uaq Nxi ninb maiq tau meib Bua.”
8.8: yem yia txb ninb Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv Tauj ib zang ninb Bua zanb zang kwavg yia, fub suj Eiag Eei zyenb. ninb Bua yaag fib Navq Eei zruj pun meib.
8.3: mq paag saa-mu-en Eei txn maiq zwrtg ninb Bua Eei tia Eei Euvg zeiq zruj. ninb Bua Kuvj trub kanb tu'q Eaanb Navq, Eang Eaanb Mwavj yaag Byenq pcvb fim Eei leid.
8.21: saa-mu-en haid pc'g fivj kxvq Eei yetg zuvq waag ninb zyrug txb naaiq teij waag mivb Buaj zyruq.
8.14: ninb xij zx'q meib Bua kaub lovj Jiaj Eei livb teig Zauj a'vung Wivj Zauj ka'lanq Wivj Jiu pun ninb Eei Jyen.
8.6: mq paag ninb Bua kxvq, “Toq pun taub huvb kunq yia Bua,” uaq teij waag, saa-mu-en haid maiq hxpg Hruq. ninb zyrug tauj kauj Buaj zyruq.
8.2: ninb Eei txnb Lo heug yo-en, txnb faij heug aa-Bi-yaa. ninb Bua i taub yem Be-e-Qe-Baa zruj tomb Jyen.
8.20: weig pun yia Bua Navq nxmb nxm kua'q Eei myenb maaib huvb tiaj kunq, yaag txb yia Bua Zwrtq mivb Bx'q Jaaj.”
8.7: zyruq tau saa-mu-en, “xij zu'g mwavj pc'g fivj Zauj meib kxvq Eei yetg zuvq waag, weig zu'g ninb Bua maiq zeid Gemb meib. ninb Bua Gemb yia, maiq lovg yia zruj ninb Bua Eei huvb.
8.19: mq paag pc'g fivj maiq Kavq mwavj saa-mu-en kxvq Eei waag. ninb Bua vcvg Jyenq kxvq, “maiq zeid! yia Bua Dovg haaij zuvq xij lovg taub huvb kunq yia Bua,
8.17: ninb xij zx'q meib Bua Eei pa'ki yuvb Zauj yuvb kwanb zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq. meib Bua yaag zu'g zruj ninb Eei nrub.
8.11: saa-mu-en kxvq, “kunq meib Bua uaq taub huvb tiaj Eei za'eij xij Navq naaiq. ninb xij zx'q meib Eei txn zruj pcv. maaib teij ninb xij Paaiq zaavq ninb Eei Bx'q Jaaj Eei maab Zia, maaib teij Paaiq zruj keb maad pcv, maaib teij Paaiq Tiuj mivb Daavg Bx'q Jaaj Eei maab Zia.
8.5: ninb Bua kxvq, “meib Eei Havb Jeiq koj a'q. meib Eei txn yaag maiq zwrtg meib Eei Euvg zeiq zruj. ib zang Toq meib lyepg taub huvb kunq yia Bua Navq nxmb nxm kua'q maaib nx.”
8.9: uaq Euvg, meib kunq ei ninb Bua Eei waag. mq paag xij zu'g lovb lovj Eei Kwinj ninb Bua, kxvq mevb pun ninb Bua hiuq tu'q xij kunq ninb Bua uaq taub huvb tiaj Eei za'eij xij Navq haiq nx.”
8.16: ninb xij zx'q meib Bua Eei mJavg pru msia'q pru Zauj kaub lovj Jiaj Eei myenb lunj myenb Zauj lxb Tevj ninb zruj kov.
8.4: i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj myenb koj zyrug kapq zunq taaib Tauj laa-maa zivb lxd saa-mu-en.
8.10: saa-mu-en zx'q zyruq kxvq Eei yetg zuvq waag zunb Buaj tovb Toq ninb Tevj lyepg huvb tiaj Eei pc'g fivj mwavj.
8.22: zyruq kxvq Buaj saa-mu-en, “kunq mwavj ninb Bua cvj lyepg taub huvb tiaj pun ninb Bua.” saa-mu-en zyrug Buaj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb, “kx'g myenb kunq Rwrnj kx'g myenb Eei pwrnb muvq a'q.”
8.12: maaib teij ninb xij Paaiq zruj yetg Zin taub pcv Eei pyeiq, maaib teij zruj Mmd zyepg taub Eei pyeiq. maaib teij xij zu'g Tevj ninb laib Dau, maaib teij Tevj ninb syru kcvb zwavj, maaib teij Tevj ninb taaq Bx'q Jaaj Eei ua'g king, maaib teij zruj maab Zia Eei Jaab sig.
8.15: ninb xij zx'q meib Bua Eei Byaub Zauj a'vung pyruq zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq pun ninb Eei Jyen Zauj pru.
8.13: ninb xij zx'q meib Bua Eei sia'q Tevj ninb zruj yrub Daav, zruq laib Naavj, zruj Fuaq.
8.1: saa-mu-en Havb Jeiq koj Eei zyavb hog, ninb lyepg ninb Eei txn zruj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei tomb Jyen.

3.18: saa-mu-en zyrug kxvq Revg yetg zuvq waag Buaj e-li, yaag maiq pivj yetg Euvg. e-li kxvq, “naaiq se zyruq a'q. Toq pun ninb zruj ziuj ninb pwatg hxpg zu'g zruj Eei.”
3.3: Tinb huvb Eei tav maiq kcvb taig. saa-mu-en pweij Jyenq zyruq Eei Dopg liub ka'Euad, Tinb huvb Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav yem uaq nxm txvj.
3.8: zyruq cvj heug saa-mu-en ta'faam Rung. saa-mu-en cvj Jiad sin taaib mivb e-li uaq yaag kxvq, “yia yem naaiq weig zu'g meib heug yia.” e-li zyrug mevb pc'g se zyruq heug naaiq taub txn.
3.19: saa-mu-en Lo Jyenq faauj, zyruq yaag Zauj ninb yem, pun ninb kxvq Eei Jrub Jruj waag maiq puvj Dxtq.
3.9: e-li zyrug kxvq Buaj saa-mu-en, “kunq mivb pweij a'q. sij kxvq ninb cvj heug meib, meib xij zu'g kxvq, ‘zyruq aag, kunq kxvq a'q. yia, meib Eei pru, mwavj Jyenq Eei.’+” saa-mu-en zyrug Rwrnj mivb pweij ninb Eei txvj.
3.7: uaq zang saa-mu-en maiq kcvb hiuq tu'q zyruq. ninb yaag maiq kcvb tu'q zipq Jiaj zyruq Eei waag.
3.5: ninb zyrug Tiuj mivb Tauj e-li uaq yaag kxvq, “meib heug yia, yia yem naaiq og.” mq paag e-li tau, “yia maiq heug meib. kunq Rwrnj mivb pweij a'q.” ninb zyrug Rwrnj mivb pweij Jyenq.
3.16: e-li zyrug heug saa-mu-en, “yia Eei txn, saa-mu-en, aag.” saa-mu-en tau, “yia yem naaiq og.”
3.20: yem Daan mivb Tauj Be-e-Qe-Baa, i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb hiuq tu'q zyruq lyepg saa-mu-en zruj ninb Eei trug waag myenb.
3.17: e-li naaig, “zyruq kxvq haiq Euvg Buaj meib? maiq tuvq pivj yia. sij kxvq meib pivj haiq Euvg maiq kxvq Buaj yia, tovb Tinb huvb kxvq Buaj meib Eei yetg zuvq waag nx, Toq Tinb huvb zruj pun meib, zuvq Niab Niaq Eei zruj.”
3.14: weig naaiq yia hruq waag pun e-li Eei zeib fun. yia kxvq, ‘e-li Eei zeib fun zruj Eei zwid yetg liud maiq maaib haiq Euvg ziag Eei ka'naaiq fai fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq haib fi'q tu'q ninb Bua Eei zwid.’+”
3.4: zyruq zyrug heug, “saa-mu-en aag, saa-mu-en!” saa-mu-en tau, “yia yem naaiq.”
3.21: zyruq cvj yem si-lo hing Zwrtq weig zu'g zyruq yem si-lo zx'q kanb Eei waag pun saa-mu-en hiuq tu'q ninb.
3.2: maaib mwrnd nx, e-li pweij Jyenq ninb kanb Eei txvj. ninb Eei mziv Buaq, mavg maiq navg zyen.
3.6: zyruq cvj heug, “saa-mu-en aag.” saa-mu-en Jiad sin taaib mivb e-li uaq cvj kxvq, “yia yem naaiq weig zu'g meib heug yia.” e-li tau, “yia Eei txn aag, yia maiq tu'q heug meib. cvj Rwrnj mivb pweij a'q.”
3.13: yia zuvq Buaj Jiaj ninb, yia xij yetg liud tivg ninb Eei zeib fun Eei zwid weig zu'g ninb hiuq tu'q ninb Eei txn Bua Eei zwid. ninb Bua Ki Tinb huvb, e-li yaag maiq paaq ninb Bua.
3.12: Tauj uaq nxm Nxi yia xij zruj zyavj pun tovb yia kxvq Jiaj e-li Eei zeib fun Eei yetg zuvq waag yem kxn Tauj setq mweid.
3.15: saa-mu-en cvj pweij Tauj luvb Fav zyrug Kxi zavg zyruq Eei pyauq Eei kcvb. saa-mu-en maiq kaamq kxvq uaq teij laaug yaavb Eei sig Buaj e-li.
3.11: zyruq kxvq Buaj saa-mu-en, “yia xij yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei Bu'Dovj zruj yetg Euvg. ta'faanb mwavj haid Eei myenb Eei i puv mnxmb zuvq xij Givj Revg.
3.1: naaiq taub txn, saa-mu-en, yem e-li Eei Ra'Myen fub suj zyruq. uaq Jaaj luvb Diaq maiq navg maaib waag yem zyruq taaib yaag maiq navg maaib hing yaavb Eei Jauq.
3.10: zyruq taaib sruq Jyenq uaq cvj Navq zinb Daavg uaq teij pua Rung nx heug, “saa-mu-en aag, saa-mu-en!” saa-mu-en tau, “kunq kxvq a'q. yia, meib Eei pru, mwavj Jyenq Eei.”

21.3: meib maaib teij haiq Euvg Eang yem meib naaiq fai? Toq pun pyaa nxm Fuaq yia fai yem meib naaiq maaib haiq Euvg Eang hopq yaag tu'q.”
21.8: Daa-witq naaig aa-hi-me-lekq, “yem naaiq meib maiq maaib yetg tiub Zav fai yetg zuv Ru'g Daauq fai? yia maiq tu'q txb Ru'g Daauq fai ua'g king taaib, weig zu'g huvb tiaj Paaiq Eei Jauq xij zu'g kaanq Jyenq taaib.”
21.9: sai myenb kxvq, “tovb meib yem e-laa hxvd taij uaq taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb, ko-li-atg, Eei Ru'g Daauq Zxg peu Jyenq Dia an Jyenq e-fotq Eei Ga'haaq mcvj. sij kxvq meib xij lovg nx, kunq zx'q txb mivb a'q. Zwrtq liud uaq zuv maiq maaib kanb zuv a'q.” Daa-witq kxvq, “maiq maaib haiq zuv Ru'g Daauq Dovg uaq zuv yaaug. Toq pun yia og,”
21.7: uaq Nxi maaib taub myenb yem uaq. ninb zruj sau-lo Eei pru, se e-Dom myenb, Buaj heug Do-ekg. ninb Zxg yem Jyenq zyruq Eei Ra'Myen uaq. ninb zruj kruj sau-lo Eei scvb Kuq pru Eei pyeiq zeiq.
21.5: Daa-witq tau sai myenb, “za'kevb nx, yia Bua haiq zang Zwrtq Jauq, yia Bua keg Jyenq msia'q txn, maiq pun taaib nitq fatq yia Bua. Zwrtq mivb weig Prub Tov Eei Jauq naaiq teij myenb lunj myenb Eei sin mtaaib Zivb Revg Eei. Navq naaig, Zwrtq mivb weig levg Jeiq Eei Jauq, ninb Bua Eei sin kaub fatq Zivb Revg.”
21.14: aa-Kitq zyrug kxvq Buaj ninb Eei pru, “mavg kaaj, meib Bua pwatg naaiq taub putg Din myenb. meib Bua txb ninb taaib lxd yia zruj haiq Euvg?
21.4: sai myenb tau Daa-witq, “yia maiq maaib Prub Tov Eei Fuaq. Kuvj maaib teij Zivb Revg Eei Fuaq Navq. ta'faanb Toq pun uaq teij myenb lunj myenb maiq tu'q pweij msia'q txn, ninb Bua Eang tu'q Eei.”
21.2: Daa-witq kxvq Buaj aa-hi-me-lekq sai myenb, “huvb tiaj Paaiq yia zruj yetg Euvg Jauq yaag kxvq Buaj yia, ‘yia Paaiq Eei waag yaag Jiu pun meib zruj Eei maiq tuvq Buaj haiq taub.’ yia Zauj kwanb myenb lunj myenb tunj zyavj txig xij pwavb yetg nxm txvj.
21.6: Navq naaig sai myenb zyrug zx'q Zivb Revg Fuaq pun Daa-witq, weig zu'g yem uaq maiq maaib kanb Euvg Fuaq. Kuvj maaib kevj liud Tinb huvb zx'q Fiag taaib Eei Fuaq. se yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen kevj liud zx'q Fiag taaib uaq Nxi Tiuq syavb Fuab Jxm uaq teij lob Fuaq.
21.13: Daa-witq zyrug Tiuq ninb Eei eij leid taaib tu'g eij zruj penj putg Din myenb, la'kwaib kwetq zivb kcvb, uamb Rwib yaag lyrug Fiag kua'q Jyenq ninb Eei syaam.
21.12: Daa-witq zyrug yem Hruq Javj Jyenq naaiq teij waag, yaag haid kamb Riaj haig katg zivb Eei huvb, aa-Kitq.
21.15: yia Qyemj zu'g putg Din myenb meib Bua Zivj taaib txb naaiq taub loq taaib yem yia Eei Ra'Myen zruj putg Din sig pun yia mavg fai? naaiq Euvg myenb Pwij tu'q pia'g yia Eei pyauq fai?”
21.11: aa-Kitq Eei pru kxvq Buaj aa-Kitq, “naaiq taub Daa-witq penj ninb Eei teib puv Eei huvb maiq zeid? se naaiq taub yem uaq Eei msia'q txn Zavj heij paauj Ruv kxvq, “+‘sau-lo taij myenb penj Zinb Zin. Daa-witq taij myenb penj waanb waang’ maiq zeid?”
21.1: Daa-witq zyrug mivb Tauj nopq muvq, aa-hi-me-lekq sai myenb uaq. aa-hi-me-lekq sin zinj Jyenq Zwrtq taaib zipq Daa-witq. ninb kxvq, “weig haiq tiug meib kanb taaib Navq, maiq maaib haiq taub Zauj meib taaib fai?”
21.10: uaq Nxi Daa-witq pyauj sau-lo yaag mivb lxd katg zivb Eei huvb, aa-Kitq.

14.18: sau-lo kxvq Buaj aa-hi-yaa, “txb Tinb huvb Eei faav taaib naaiq,” (weig zu'g uaq zang Tinb huvb Eei faav Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb yem.)
14.45: pc'g fivj naaig sau-lo, “yo-naa-Taan za'kevb xij zu'g taig fai? ninb yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj Tevj Bua tu'q hivb Jiaj. yia Bua zyavq Jyenq zyavb Jyenq Eei zyruq lcvd waag, yo-naa-Taan Eei yetg tiub Ba'pyei zuvq maiq zu'g Dxtq Fiag Dau, weig zu'g ninb ib Nxi Zauj Tinb huvb Jwavg Jyenq Bx'q Jaaj.” pc'g fivj siaj Zwrtq yo-naa-Taan Eei mcvg, ninb zyrug maiq zu'g taij taig.
14.3: yem uaq teij myenb ka'Euad maaib aa-hi-yaa zu'q Jyenq e-fotq. aa-hi-yaa se i-Kaa-Botg Eei kxj, aa-hi-Tupq Eei txn, fi-ne-hatg Eei fun, e-li sai myenb Eei fa'q. zinb Daavg e-li yem si-lo zruj zyruq Eei sai myenb. uaq teij myenb zuvq maiq hiuq tu'q yo-naa-Taan mivb mig a'q.
14.43: sau-lo zyrug naaig yo-naa-Taan, “meib zruj haiq Euvg? Buaj yia maa'b!” yo-naa-Taan tau, “yia tu'q seij ti'q tyen kua'q Jyenq yia nanq Eei pyaaq tweib mweid Eei mweib txvb Navq. yia yem naaiq, yia xij zu'g taig a'q.”
14.50: sau-lo Eei auq, Buaj heug aa-hi-no-am, se aa-hi-maa-atg Eei sia'q. sau-lo Eei tomb pcvb pyeiq Eei Buaj heug apg-ne, se ne Eei txn. ne se sau-lo Eei pc'q.
14.14: yo-naa-Taan Zauj Tevj ninb txb ua'g king uaq taub myenb taij taaub Rung fi-li-saa-tia myenb maaib leib maiq ko Eig zyepg taub myenb yem Dovg yetg txij vovb laib yetg aanj Eei Dau Javq ka'Euad.
14.48: huvb tiaj Bx'q Jaaj henq, yaag Bx'q aa-maa-lekq myenb, Fruj i-saa-laa-en myenb pyauj Dutq luq ninb Bua uaq teij myenb Eei puab Diaq.
14.34: sau-lo cvj kxvq, “kaanq mivb zwavj myenb Bu'Dovj Buaj ninb Bua, ‘kx'g myenb txb kanb Eei vovb fai pa'ki yuvb taaib yem naaiq taij, yem naaiq Eang. maiq tuvq Eang xq zxpg Jyenq Ryaamq zyrug paamd zwid txvg zyruq. ’+” uaq mwrnd taub taub myenb zyrug txb ninb Bua Eei vovb taaib yem uaq taij.
14.2: uaq zang sau-lo yem ki-Be-aa zivb Len, mi-kon teig Eei yetg zuvb zi'g lyrub Dyavj ka'Diaq. kan ninb Eei myenb maaib leib maiq ko lua'g pc'q taub.
14.36: sau-lo kxvq, “Bua luvb mwrnd zang Fiag mivb zung fi-li-saa-tia myenb, Zaavq ninb Bua Eei ka'naaiq Tauj luvb Fav. Bua zuvq maiq lyrub ninb Bua yetg taub.” pc'g fivj tau, “ziuj meib pwatg hxpg zu'g zruj Eei kunq zruj a'q.” mq paag sai myenb kxvq, “Bua xij zu'g yem naaiq, naaig zyruq Daavg.”
14.35: sau-lo weig zyruq Zeij nxm ziab txvb. naaiq se ninb weig zyruq Zeij Eei taaub nxm ziab txvb.
14.24: uaq Nxi i-saa-laa-en myenb za'kevb Kruq haig, weig zu'g sau-lo heug pc'g fivj hruq waag kxvq, “ib Nxi maiq kcvb Mwavj yaag maiq kcvb tu'q Jaauq win pun yia Eei winb wavq nx, ta'faanb haiq taub Eang haiq Euvg ka'naaiq, uaq taub xij zu'g zyruj a'q.” weig naaiq zyavb Nxi maiq maaib haiq taub tu'q Eang haiq Euvg.
14.7: Tevj ninb txb ua'g king uaq taub kxvq Buaj ninb, “ziuj meib Eei Hruq pwatg hxpg zu'g zruj Eei, kunq zruj a'q. yia kan meib. meib Eei Hruq Navq haiq nx, yia yaag Navq uaq nx.”
14.17: sau-lo zyrug kxvq Buaj kan ninb uaq teij myenb, “saauq mavg kaaj, maaib haiq taub yem Bua naaiq Zwrtq mivb?” ninb Bua saauq zyrug hiuq tu'q yo-naa-Taan Zauj Tevj ninb txb ua'g king uaq taub txn maiq yem naaig.
14.49: sau-lo Eei txn maaib yo-naa-Taan, itg-wi Zauj man-Ki-su-waa. ninb cvj maaib i taub sia'q. sia'g Lo Eei Buaj heug me-laapq, sia'g faij heug mi-Kaan.
14.11: ninb Bua i taub zyrug Zwrtq taaib pun fi-li-saa-tia pcv Eei Zyavq uaq teij pcv pwatg. fi-li-saa-tia myenb kxvq, “mavg maa'b! hipq-lu myenb yem ninb Bua pivj Eei Kwrtq Zwrtq taaib a'q.”
14.33: maaib myenb Buaj sau-lo, “mavg maa'b! zwavj pc'g fivj paamd zwid txvg zyruq weig zu'g ninb Bua Eang xq zxpg Jyenq Ryaamq.” sau-lo zyrug kxvq, “meib Bua zruj Byenq Hruq Eei sig a'q. zx'q nxm tomb la'pyeiq Favj Tauj yia naaiq.”
14.16: yem Ben-yaa-min teig Eei ki-Be-aa zivb, sau-lo Eei syruq kcv myenb mavg pwatg pcv faatq Raanj Eei Jiaj mivb Jiaj taaib Eei.
14.40: huvb tiaj zyrug kxvq Buaj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb, “meib Bua yetg zuvq yem yetg puv. yia Zauj yia Eei txn, yo-naa-Taan, kanb yem yetg puv.” pc'g fivj zyrug tau sau-lo, “ziuj huvb tiaj pwatg hxpg zu'g zruj Eei kunq zruj a'q.”
14.37: sau-lo zyrug naaig Tinb huvb, “yia mivb zung fi-li-saa-tia myenb se hxpg fai maiq hxpg? meib xij zx'q ninb Bua Jiu pun yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei puab Diaq Eei fai?” mq paag uaq Nxi Tinb huvb maiq tau ninb.
14.4: yo-naa-Taan xij yavb Jiaj Bovb Qavj uaq tiub Jauq mivb Tauj fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei pcv Eei Zyavq. uaq tiub Jauq i puv Jaub Len, yetg puv maaib nxm tomb Bcvb Zitq. maaib nxm heug Bo-setq, maaib nxm heug sej-ne.
14.51: sau-lo Eei tia, Kitq, Zauj apg-ne Eei tia, ne, zruj aa-Bi-en Eei txn.
14.12: yem zaamg Eei pcv zyrug heug yo-naa-Taan Zauj Tevj ninb txb ua'g king uaq taub txn. ninb Bua kxvq, “faauj yia Bua naaiq taaib maa'b! yia Bua maaib waag xij Buaj meib Bua.” yo-naa-Taan zyrug kxvq Buaj Tevj ninb txb ua'g king uaq taub txn, “meib kan yia faauj maa'b! weig zu'g zyruq zx'q ninb Bua Jiu pun yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei puab Diaq mig a'q.”
14.46: sau-lo zyrug tivb Fiag, maiq zung fi-li-saa-tia myenb. fi-li-saa-tia myenb zyrug Rwrnj ninb Bua kanb Eei teib puv mig a'q.
14.13: yo-naa-Taan zyrug Exv Jyenq faauj mivb. Tevj ninb txb ua'g king uaq taub yaag kan Jyenq ninb mivb. yo-naa-Taan taij fi-li-saa-tia myenb yem ninb Eei Ra'Myen Kiv Fiag. Tevj yo-naa-Taan txb ua'g king uaq taub txn yaag Tevj Jyenq ninb taij.
14.26: ninb Bua pia'g lomg uaq zang, pwatg maaib mweib txvb lyrug Zwrtq mq paag maiq maaib haiq taub lovg puad zx'q taaib Eang, weig zu'g ninb Bua kamb Riaj uaq teij hruq Eei waag.
14.28: yem uaq Eei myenb maaib taub kxvq Buaj yo-naa-Taan, “meib Eei tia hatg zwavj myenb hruq Jyenq kxvq, ‘ib Nxi haiq taub Eang haiq Euvg, uaq taub xij zu'g zyruj a'q.’+” weig naaiq zwavj myenb za'kevb mau haig.
14.8: yo-naa-Taan kxvq, “Bua Jiaj Tauj uaq teij myenb uaq yaag pun ninb Bua tu'q pwatg Bua.
14.9: sij kxvq ninb Bua kxvq Buaj Bua, ‘zuaq yia Bua mivb meib Bua naaig,’ Bua zyrug sruq tivg Bua yem Eei txvj, maiq mivb ninb Bua uaq.
14.32: zwavj myenb zyrug Waavb Waav zaavb zaav Eei Tiuj pia'g mivb lxd Zaavq tu'q taaib Eei ka'naaiq, zx'q pa'ki yuvb, vovb Zauj vovb txn yem uaq Dau taij taaib zyrug Eang xq zxpg Jyenq Ryaamq.
14.21: tovb zinb Daavg Zauj fi-li-saa-tia myenb yem yaag Zauj ninb Bua pia'g ninb Bua Eei Zyavq, uaq teij hipq-lu myenb, taauj Rwrnj taaib pia'g tovb kan sau-lo Zauj yo-naa-Taan Eei i-saa-laa-en myenb.
14.23: uaq Nxi zyruq Fruj i-saa-laa-en myenb. Bx'q Jaaj Eei Jauq zuvq Jiaj Daavg Betg-aa-wen teig uaq puv.
14.6: yo-naa-Taan kxvq Buaj Tevj ninb txb Bx'q Jaaj Eei ua'g king uaq taub myenb lunj myenb, “taaib maa'b! Bua Jiaj mivb lxd tovb maiq Jiaj kaatq Eei leid uaq teij pcv Eei Zyavq. Riaj zyruq xij Tevj Bua, weig zu'g maiq maaib haiq Euvg haib tavq tu'q Jyenq zyruq. maiq kunq myenb Zamq fai zo'g ninb zuvq haib Tevj Bua hivb.”
14.44: sau-lo kxvq, “yo-naa-Taan aa'b! meib Dovg haaij zuvq xij zu'g taig a'q. sij kxvq meib maiq taig Toq Tinb huvb Niab Niaq Eei zruj pun yia.”
14.20: sau-lo Zauj kan ninb Eei pcv zyrug kapq zunq mivb uaq Bx'q Jaaj Zyavq. mavg maa'b! fi-li-saa-tia myenb kanb lovg Ru'g Daauq laanb taij laanb. za'kevb lung Tauj Diaq a'q.
14.5: yetg nxm Bcvb Zitq yem pa'q puv nitq mikq-maatq. maaib nxm yem naamb puv nitq ke-Baa uaq puv.
14.19: sau-lo Zauj aa-hi-yaa sai myenb kxvq waag uaq zang, yem fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei Zyavq lung Eei Qiaj kunq zruj kunq Bwi. sau-lo zyrug kxvq Buaj sai myenb, “Lwrtq puad Fiag maa'b!”
14.38: sau-lo zyrug kxvq, “pc'g fivj Eei zwavj pyeiq zeiq taaib naaiq maa'b! meib Bua xij zu'g hiuq yaag xij zu'g pwatg ib Nxi naaiq teij zwid Navq haiq nx Zwrtq taaib.
14.31: uaq Nxi i-saa-laa-en myenb taij fi-li-saa-tia myenb yem mikq-maatq taij Jyenq mivb Tauj ai-yaa-lon. zwavj pcv za'kevb mau tu'q Kruq haig.
14.52: yem sau-lo Eei seij zeiq zanb zang Zauj fi-li-saa-tia myenb maaib Bx'q tomb Jaaj Eei sig. sau-lo pwatg haiq taub zyavb tu'q henq, maaib Qa'q, zyrug txb taaib kan ninb.
14.27: mq paag yo-naa-Taan maiq tu'q haid ninb Eei tia heug pc'g fivj hruq waag, ninb zyrug suv ninb nanq Eei pyaaq pa'q mweib Pevj yaag lovg puad zx'q taaib tapq Rwib. ninb Eei mziv zyrug Fav taaib a'q.
14.41: Navq naaiq sau-lo zyrug tauj kauj naaig zyruq, i-saa-laa-en Eei Tinb huvb, “Toq pun Ziv haiq puv hxpg.” Dxtq zu'g sau-lo Zauj yo-naa-Taan uaq puv, mq paag pun Ziv pc'g fivj maiq txvg.
14.1: maaib Nxi sau-lo Eei txn, yo-naa-Taan, kxvq Buaj Tevj ninb txb Bx'q Jaaj Eei ua'g king uaq taub myenb lunj myenb, “taaib maa'b! Bua Jiaj uaq vaang fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei Zyavq.” mq paag ninb maiq Buaj ninb Eei tia.
14.39: yia zyavq Jyenq zyavb Jyenq Eei zyruq, tovb Fruj i-saa- laa-en myenb uaq taub, lcvd waag, maiq kunq yia Eei txn, yo-naa-Taan, zruj txvg, ninb Dovg haaij zuvq xij zu'g taig.” mq paag yem uaq teij zwavj myenb Bu'Dovj maiq maaib yetg taub tau ninb.
14.47: sau-lo kunq i-saa-laa-en kua'q uaq zang, ninb tu'q Bx'q weib kxmj ninb uaq teij winb wavq. ninb Bx'q mo-apg myenb, am-mon myenb, e-Dom myenb Zauj yem soj-Baa Eei huvb tiaj Zauj fi-li-saa-tia myenb. maiq kunq ninb Win mivb haiq puv, ninb zyrug Bx'q tu'q hivb winb wavq.
14.10: mq paag sij kxvq ninb Bua kxvq, ‘kunq faauj taaib yia Bua naaiq maa'b!’ Bua zyrug mivb uaq a'q, weig zu'g zyruq zx'q ninb Bua Jiu pun yem Bua Eei puab Diaq mig a'q. naaiq teij sig zyrug weig Bua zruj Javb hog.”
14.25: zwavj pc'g fivj pia'g ka'Euad lomg mivb, pwatg maaib mweib txvb yem uaq Dau.
14.22: tovb pivj Jyenq e-faa-im Bovb aiq txvj uaq teij i-saa-laa-en myenb haid fyenj kxvq fi-li-saa-tia myenb pyauj, ninb Bua zyrug Zwrtq taaib zung Jyenq Bx'q Jyenq ninb Bua mivb.
14.42: sau-lo kxvq, “cvj tivg Rung mavg kaaj yia fai yia Eei txn, yo-naa-Taan.” zyrug Dxtq zu'g yo-naa-Taan.
14.15: yem Zyavq ka'Euad, yem Deig, yem zwavj myenb Bu'Dovj lung Revg. yem kruj teib puv pcv Eei zaamg, lyemb za'g pcv kwanb sin zinj Revg. Dau yaag tovd tu'q seij haig. haiq Euvg yaag za'kevb lung Revg.
14.29: yo-naa-Taan kxvq, “yia Eei tia zruj pun teib puv zu'g Kruq Navq. mavg kaaj, yia seij liud ti'q tyen naaiq teij mweib txvb, yia Eei mziv zyrug Dovg haaij Fav.
14.30: sij kxvq ib Nxi pc'g fivj tu'q sweib eij Eang yem winb wavq Zaavq taaib Eei ka'naaiq nx, kaub lovj tu'q Zamq. weig zu'g taij taig fi-li-saa-tia myenb maiq tu'q Dovg haaij Zamq a'q.”

23.18: ninb Bua i taub zyrug txv Jyenq zyruq lcvd vcvg waag. Daa-witq Zxg yem Jyenq uaq ho-letq, yo-naa-Taan Rwrnj huvb ting mig a'q.
23.8: sau-lo heug ninb Eei yetg zuvq pcv Zwrtq mivb Bx'q Jaaj, xij mivb Ke-i-laa muvq weib Jyenq Daa-witq Zauj kan ninb Eei myenb.
23.3: mq paag Daa-witq Eei myenb kxvq Buaj ninb, “yia Bua yem naaiq yu-Daa, yia Bua zuvq haid kamb Riaj Eei. sij kxvq yia Bua mivb Ke-i-laa muvq Bx'q fi-li-saa-tia myenb, yia Bua kaub fatq kamb Riaj”
23.21: sau-lo tau, “Toq zyruq Zeij fu'q pun meib Bua, weig zu'g meib Bua Kxb lyenb yia.
23.14: Daa-witq mivb yem uaq teib puvb Waav wrnq Eei txvj, se yem uaq sipg-aa teib puvb Waav Eei Bovb aiq. sau-lo Nxib Nxi zimb lxd ninb, mq paag Tinb huvb maiq zx'q ninb Jiu pun yem sau-lo Eei puab Diaq.
23.23: Navq naaig, mivb samj mavg ninb pivj Eei nxmb nxm txvj, txb zyen waag Rwrnj taaib kxvq Buaj yia, yia zyrug Zauj Jyenq meib Bua mivb. sij kxvq ninb Zxg yem yu-Daa teig nx, yia zyrug yem Zinb Zin waanb waang taub yu-Daa myenb Bu'Dovj lxd pwatg ninb.”
23.6: Ga'haaq aa-hi-me-lekq Eei txn, aa-Bi-yaa-Taa, pyauj mivb Ke-i-laa muvq lxd Daa-witq uaq zang ninb txb Jyenq e-fotq mivb.
23.2: Daa-witq zyrug naaig zyruq, “yia xij zu'g mivb Bx'q fi-li-saa-tia myenb hxpg fai maiq hxpg?”   zyruq kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “kunq mivb Bx'q fi-li-saa-tia myenb yaag Fruj Ke-i-laa muvq maa'b!”
23.20: o huvb tiaj aa'b! kunq ziuj meib kanb Eei Hruq taaib, yia Bua lcvd zx'q ninb Jiu pun huvb tiaj.”
23.24: uaq teij myenb zyrug mivb sipg-aa muvq Daavg sau-lo. uaq zang Daa-witq Zauj ninb Eei myenb yem maa-on teib puvb Waav, aa-laa-Baa ka'Euad, ye-si-mon Eei naamb puv mcvj.
23.28: sau-lo zyrug tivb, maiq zung Daa-witq. ninb taauj Gaav Rwrnj mivb Zauj fi-li-saa-tia myenb Bx'q Jaaj. weig naaiq myenb Zwrtq uaq nxm txvj Eei Buaj heug, se-laa-ham-maa-le-Kotq.
23.7: maaib myenb Buaj sau-lo, Daa-witq mivb Tauj Ke-i-laa muvq. sau-lo zyrug kxvq, “Tinb huvb zx'q ninb Jiu pun yem yia Eei puab Diaq mig a'q, weig zu'g ninb pia'g uaq nxm muvq maaib kcvb maaib kcvb sxn, ninb zyrug wrnj Jyenq ninb kanb a'q.”
23.29: Daa-witq zyrug yem naaig Zwrtq mivb yem en-ke-Di weib wrnq Eei txvj.
23.19: sipg-aa myenb mivb ki-Be-aa zivb lxd sau-lo Buaj ninb, “Daa-witq pivj Jyenq yem yia Bua Eei teib puv, ho-letq uaq, se yem haa-Ki-laa Bov, ye-si-mon teig Eei naamb puv maiq zeid fai?
23.17: yo-naa-Taan kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “maiq tuvq kamb Riaj og. yia Eei tia, sau-lo, zuvq maiq haib hxig meib. meib xij tu'q zruj huvb kunq i-saa-laa-en myenb. yia zruj ta'Eeig uaq taub. yia Eei tia, sau-lo, yaag hiuq tu'q Revg naaiq teij sig a'q.”
23.27: mq paag maaib taub trug fyenj myenb taaib kxvq Buaj sau-lo, “huvb tiaj aa'b! fi-li-saa-tia myenb txb pcv taaib Zaavq teib puv aaq lo'b! Toq huvb tiaj syepg syepq Eei Rwrnj.”
23.11: Ke-i-laa Eei pc'g fivj xij zx'q yia Zauj kan yia Eei myenb Jiu pun yem sau-lo Eei puab Diaq Eei fai? sau-lo za'kevb xij taaib taij yia, meib Eei pru, Navq yia haid nx fai? zyruq, i-saa-laa-en Eei Tinb huvb aa'b! Toq Buaj yia, meib Eei pru, maa'b!”   zyruq kxvq, “ninb xij taaib Eei.”
23.5: Daa-witq Zauj ninb Eei myenb zyrug mivb Ke-i-laa Bx'q fi-li-saa-tia myenb, Zaavq ninb Bua Eei scvb Kuq yaag taij fi-li-saa-tia myenb taig Zamq haig. ninb yaag Fruj Ke-i-laa muvq Eei myenb.
23.9: Daa-witq hiuq tu'q sau-lo taaq za'eij hxig ninb, ninb zyrug kxvq Buaj aa-Bi-yaa-Taa sai myenb, “txb e-fotq taaib naaiq maa'b!”
23.16: sau-lo Eei txn, yo-naa-Taan, zyrug mivb ho-letq lxd Daa-witq, yaag Tevj Daa-witq Kauj Tinb huvb henq Jyenq faauj.
23.4: Daa-witq cvj naaig Rung zyruq.  zyruq tau ninb, “meib kunq mivb Ke-i-laa, weig zu'g yia xij zx'q fi-li-saa-tia myenb Jiu pun yem meib Eei puab Diaq.”
23.10: Daa-witq zyrug naaig, “o zyruq i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei Tinb huvb aa'b! yia, meib Eei pru, haid kxvq sau-lo za'kevb taaq za'eij taaib naaiq Ke-i-laa yaag laaij yia, ninb xij myetg Revg naaiq nxm muvq.
23.22: Toq meib Bua lovb lovj Eei zaab mavg ninb pivj Eei nxmb nxm txvj, yaag mavg kaaj haiq taub pwatg ninb yem naaig, weig zu'g yia haid myenb kxvq ninb kuq kwaij haig.
23.12: Daa-witq cvj naaig, “Ke-i-laa Eei pc'g fivj xij zx'q yia Zauj kan yia Eei myenb Jiu pun yem sau-lo Eei puab Diaq fai?”   zyruq tau, “ninb Bua xij zx'q meib Bua Jiu pun a'q.”
23.15: Daa-witq hiuq tu'q sau-lo Zwrtq taaib xij zx'q ninb Eei mcvg. uaq zang Daa-witq yem sipg-aa teib puvb Waav, ho-letq uaq.

20.40: yo-naa-Taan zyrug zx'q Jwavb zinj Zauj fxv pun uaq taub txn, heug ninb, “Rwrnj a'q. txb naaiq teij ka'naaiq Rwrnj uaq zivb a'q.”
20.14: sij kxvq yia Zxg maaib mcvg zyavb Jyenq, Toq meib Navq zyruq zyepg zua'q Eei zruj lovj pun yia maiq zu'g taig.
20.23: Navq naaig yia Zauj meib kxvq naaiq teij Jaub lrug, Toq zyruq yem yia Bua Bu'Dovj yetg liud zruj zxvb zevj.”
20.6: sij kxvq meib Eei tia pwatg yia maiq yem naaig tiab nx, Toq meib Tevj Buaj huvb tiaj, ‘Daa-witq Toq yia pun ninb kaanq Rwrnj ninb kanb Eei pwrnb muvq, Betg-le-hem muvq, weig zu'g yem uaq ninb Eei pyauq zov myenb fovg hxg Havb Havj ziag Eei ka'naaiq.’
20.34: yo-naa-Taan za'kevb Qiaj Jiad haig, zyrug Jiad sin taaib Fiag tiab mig a'q. scvb Eeig uaq Nxi maiq Eang Naavj a'q, weig zu'g ninb Raub haig Daa-witq, yaag weig zu'g ninb Eei tia Dovg naaig paaig Daa-witq Eei Myen.
20.2: yo-naa-Taan tau ninb, “zuvq maiq maaib! meib maiq zu'g taig lx'g. yia Eei tia zruj haiq Euvg maiq kunq sig Lo fai faij, maiq maaib yetg Euvg ninb maiq pun yia hiuq. yia Eei tia fuvg pivj naaiq teij sig maiq Buaj yia? taaij maiq zeid Navq naaig saa'b?”
20.36: yo-naa-Taan Buaj uaq taub txn, “Tiuj mivb Raud yia pwrnq mivb Eei fxv og.” uaq taub txn Tiuj mivb uaq zang, yo-naa-Taan zyrug pwrnq Ritq fxv mivb Dxtq uaq taub txn Eei uaq Daavg mcvj.
20.20: yia xij huvj Jyenq uaq nxm la'pyeiq ka'Len pwrnq pua Ritq fxv Navq pwrnq Bc'g nx.
20.24: Daa-witq zyrug mivb pivj uaq lomb Waav. Tauj scvb yetq Nxi, huvb tiaj zyrug zweid Jyenq tiab Eang Naavj.
20.28: yo-naa-Taan tau sau-lo, “Daa-witq Qa'q Toq yia pun ninb Rwrnj Betg-le-hem.
20.7: sij kxvq huvb tiaj kxvq, ‘lovj a'q,’ yia, meib Eei pru, zyrug yem lovj. mq paag sij kxvq ninb Qiaj Jiad nx, meib zyrug hiuq tu'q ninb Dovg haaij zuvq xij hxig yia.
20.29: ninb kxvq, ‘Toq pun yia mivb, weig zu'g yia Eei pyauq zov myenb yem uaq nxm muvq fovg hxg ziag. yia Eei kxj Bua heug yia xij zu'g mivb. sij kxvq meib pwatg hxpg nx, Toq pun yia Rwrnj mivb mavg yia Eei kxj Bua.’ weig naaiq ninb Zivj taaib maiq tu'q taaib Zauj huvb tiaj Jwavg tiab Eang Naavj.”
20.19: Naav Nxi xij zu'g syepg syepq Eei Fiag mivb Tauj meib zinb Daavg pivj Eei txvj, yem e-sen Eei la'pyeiq ka'Len zuaq Jyenq.
20.17: yo-naa-Taan Namq Daa-witq zyrug pun Daa-witq cvj lcvd Rung waag, weig zu'g ninb Namq Daa-witq, Dovg Namq kanb Eei mcvg.
20.38: yo-naa-Taan cvj heug Jyenq Buaj uaq taub txn, “kaanq syepg syepq Eei mivb. maiq tuvq vaib.” uaq taub txn zyrug Raud fxv taaib, Rwrnj ninb Eei zyruq uaq.
20.31: ta'faanb Jyetg-si Eei txn Zxg maaib mcvg zyavb naaiq nxm luvb Diaq nx, meib kanb fai meib Eei kua'q maiq haib lyepg tu'q wrnq a'q. ib zang Paaiq myenb mivb txb ninb taaib yia naaiq. ninb Dovg haaij zuvq xij zu'g taig a'q.”
20.30: sau-lo zyrug Qiaj Jiad! haig yo-naa-Taan. sau-lo kxvq, “meib naaig taub Byenq Hruq, kuq kwaij msia'q txn Eei fu'Jweiq aa'b! yia fuvg maiq hiuq tu'q meib kinq Jyetg-si Eei txn zruj pun meib kanb zu'g Eaiq, pun meib kanb Eei maa zu'g paaig Myen.
20.27: mq paag ta'Eeig Nxi, se scvb Eeig uaq Nxi, Daa-witq Eei txvj Zxg Kuvj Eei. sau-lo zyrug naaig ninb Eei txn, yo-naa-Taan, “Jyetg-si Eei txn a'Nxi Zauj ib Nxi weig haiq tiug maiq taaib Eang Naavj?”
20.11: yo-naa-Taan tau Daa-witq, “taaib maa'b! Bua mivb uaq lomb Waav.” ninb Bua i taub zyrug mivb lomb Waav a'q.
20.5: Daa-witq zyrug Buaj yo-naa-Taan, “Fav Nxi se scvb yetq Nxi. yia xij zu'g Zauj huvb tiaj Jwavg tiab Eang Naavj, mq paag Toq pun yia mivb pivj Jyenq uaq lomb Waav Tauj scvb faam uaq Nxi luvb maanb Mwavj.
20.9: yo-naa-Taan zyrug kxvq, “maiq tuvq pun maaib naaiq teij sig Zwrtq, sij kxvq yia hiuq tu'q yia Eei tia Jiad Hruq hxig meib, yia fuvg maiq kxvq Buaj meib?”
20.16: yo-naa-Taan zyrug Zauj Daa-witq, lyemb weig ninb Eei zeib fun, lcvd Jiad vcvg waag, yaag kxvq “Toq zyruq Jaauq win pun Daa-witq Eei yetg zuvq winb wavq.”
20.41: uaq taub txn yetq mivb liud, Daa-witq zyrug yem uaq nxm la'pyeiq Eei naamb puv Zwrtq taaib yaag Pua'q Fiag Myen Tauj Dau paaij yo-naa-Taan pua paaij. ninb Bua i taub zyrug zom Jaaj yaag Eyemq mq paag Daa-witq Eyemq kaub Zamq.
20.37: uaq taub txn mivb Tauj yo-naa-Taan Eei fxv Dxtq Eei txvj, yo-naa-Taan heug Jyenq kxvq, “fxv maiq zeid yem meib Eei uaq Daavg fai?”
20.39: mq paag uaq taub txn maiq hiuq tu'q naaiq teij Jaub lrug. Kuvj yo-naa-Taan Zauj Daa-witq kanb hiuq Navq.
20.4: yo-naa-Taan zyrug kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “meib Navq haiq nx Buaj yia, yia zyrug weig meib Navq uaq nx zruj.”
20.10: Daa-witq zyrug kxvq Buaj yo-naa-Taan, “sij kxvq meib Eei tia kxvq Zyruq pun meib nx, haiq taub haib Buaj yia?”
20.22: sij kxvq yia Buaj uaq taub txn, ‘mavg maa'b! fxv yem meib Eei uaq Daavg mcvj,’ nx, meib xij zu'g mivb a'q, weig zu'g zyruq Paaiq meib mivb.
20.12: yo-naa-Taan kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “Toq zyruq, i-saa-laa-en Eei Tinb huvb, Tevj zruj zxvb zevj. Fav Nxi leib maiq ko naaiq nxm zyavb hog, fai Tauj ta'faam Nxi, yia xij seij yia Eei tia Eei Hruq. sij kxvq maaib Hruq zruj lovj pun Daa-witq nx, yia zyrug Paaiq myenb mivb Buaj meib.
20.42: yo-naa-Taan kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “kunq pcvb xn Eei mivb a'q, weig zu'g Bua i taub zyavq Jyenq zyruq Eei Buaj lcvd vcvg waag kxvq, ‘Toq zyruq yem meib Zauj yia Bu'Dovj, yaag yem meib Eei zeib fun Zauj yia Eei zeib fun Bu'Dovj, yetg liud zruj zxvb zevj.’+” Daa-witq zyrug mivb mig a'q. yo-naa-Taan yaag Rwrnj uaq zivb a'q.
20.15: zyruq myetg Revg yem Daub peib meib Eei yetg zuvq winb wavq uaq zang, Toq meib yetg liud zyepg zua'q Eei zruj lovj pun yia Eei zeib fun.”
20.13: mq paag sij kxvq yia Eei tia maaib Hruq xij hxig meib Eei mcvg, yia yaag maiq pun meib hiuq, maiq Tevj meib pcvb xn Eei pyauj Dutq nx, Toq zyruq Niab Niaq Eei tivg yia, yo-naa-Taan, Eei zwid. Toq zyruq Zauj meib yem, Navq zinb Daavg Zauj yia Eei tia yem nx.
20.1: Daa-witq yem laa-maa zivb, naa-yotq uaq pyauj mivb lxd yo-naa-Taan. Daa-witq kxvq, “yia zruj haiq Euvg fai? yia txvg haiq Euvg zwid? yia zruj haiq Euvg txvg meib Eei tia ninb Zivj taaib xij zx'q yia Eei mcvg?”
20.26: uaq Nxi sau-lo maiq kxvq haiq Euvg weig zu'g ninb yem Hruq Namq, “Riaj Daa-witq pwavb zu'g sig. taaij ninb maaib wij, ninb Dovg haaij zuvq maiq Zivb Revg.”
20.25: huvb tiaj zweid Jyenq ninb yetg kau zweid Eei txvj nitq Jyenq Fovg. yo-naa-Taan txij Myen zweid, apg-ne zweid sau-lo Eei ka'Len, mq paag Daa-witq Eei txvj Kuvb Kuvj uaq.

24.18: ib Nxi meib pun Ziv meib Navq haiq nx zruj lovj pun yia, weig zu'g zyruq zx'q yia Jiu pun yem meib Eei puab Diaq mq paag meib maiq hxig yia.
24.8: Ga'haaq Daa-witq Zwrtq Bcvb Kwrtq mivb heug sau-lo, “yia Eei zyruq, huvb tiaj aa'b!” sau-lo Winb Rwrnj mavg. Daa-witq zyrug Pua'q Fiag Dau paaij sau-lo.
24.3: sau-lo taaib Tauj yem Jaub Len uaq teij pa'ki yuvb laanb. yem uaq nxm txvj maaib nxm Bcvb Kwrtq. sau-lo zyrug pia'g Bcvb Kwrtq mivb Jaiq puad. Daa-witq Zauj ninb Eei myenb yaag zweid Jyenq Bcvb Kwrtq ka'Euad Do Jiaj Eei txvj.
24.21: weig naaiq Toq meib zyavq Jyenq zyruq lcvd waag Buaj yia, meib maiq Pai kwavg yia Eei zeib fun yaag maiq yem yia Eei tia Eei trub zov sxtq yia Eei Buaj kwavg.”
24.14: “i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei huvb tiaj Zwrtq taaib lxd haiq taub? zung haiq taub? Kuvj zung taub Jub taig, zung nxm Jub mua saa'b?
24.6: ninb kxvq Buaj Zauj ninb yem uaq teij myenb, “Toq zyruq paaq Jyenq maiq tuvq pun yia cvj Navq naaiq nx zruj pun yia Eei zyruq, tovb zyruq lovg yrub xn taaib Eei myenb. maiq tuvq pun yia zruj haiq Euvg hxig ninb, weig zu'g ninb se zyruq xn taaib Eei myenb.”
24.2: sau-lo zyrug txb ninb yem i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb Bu'Dovj kinq taaib Eei pua Zin taub henq Eei pcv mivb Tauj Yiab yuvb Bcvj lxd Daa-witq Zauj kan Daa-witq Eei myenb.
24.20: ib zang yia hiuq tu'q, meib Dovg haaij zuvq tu'q zruj huvb. i-saa-laa-en kua'q xij zu'g yem meib Eei puab Diaq lyepg Jiad.
24.7: Daa-witq yaag lovg naaiq teij waag laanb Jyenq kan ninb Eei myenb, yaag maiq pun haiq taub myenb zruj haiq Euvg hxig sau-lo. sau-lo zyrug Jiad sin Zwrtq Bcvb Kwrtq kan ninb Eei Jauq mivb mig a'q.
24.19: weig zu'g maiq maaib haiq taub pwavb ninb Eei winb wavq Zxg cvj puvj ninb pcvb xn Eei mivb. Navq naaig Toq zyruq zruj lovj winb pun meib Navq meib ib Nxi zruj lovj pun yia.
24.17: ninb kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “meib kaub lovj yia, weig zu'g meib zruj lovj pun yia, mq paag yia zruj x'q pun meib.
24.11: yia Eei tia aa'b! mavg maa'b! meib Eei lwib syaamb Jia'q Eei kx'q yem yia Eei puad, weig zu'g yia kaatq meib Eei lwib syaamb Jia'q mq paag maiq taij meib. ib zang meib mevb pc'g yaag hiuq tu'q. yia maiq zruj txvg, yaag maiq vcvg huvb tiaj. yia maiq zruj haiq Euvg txvg huvb tiaj, mq paag meib zung yia xij zx'q yia Eei mcvg.
24.5: Ga'haaq Daa-witq haid Hruq maiq lovj, weig zu'g ninb kaatq sau-lo Eei lwib syaamb Jia'q Eei kx'q.
24.9: Daa-witq kxvq Buaj sau-lo, “huvb tiaj weig haiq tiug mwavj myenb kxvq, Daa-witq xij hxig huvb tiaj Eei mcvg?
24.16: Daa-witq kxvq naaiq teij waag pun sau-lo mwavj liud, sau-lo kxvq, “yia Eei txn, Daa-witq aag, naaiq se meib Eei Qiaj fai?” sau-lo zyrug Eyemq tu'q Bwi haig.
24.4: Daa-witq Eei myenb kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “ib Nxi se tovb zyruq kxvq Buaj meib, ‘yia xij zx'q meib Eei winb wavq Jiu pun yem meib Eei puab Diaq. meib kunq sweib eij zruj pun ninb a'q.’+” Daa-witq zyrug Jiad sin taaib hevb hev Eei mivb Tauj sau-lo Eei Ga'haaq Gaav zyrug kaatq nxm sau-lo Eei lwib syaamb Jia'q Eei kx'q Dutq mivb. sau-lo yaag maiq hiuq tu'q.
24.10: ib Nxi huvb tiaj kanb Eei mziv tu'q pwatg liud yem Bcvb Kwrtq zyruq zuvq zx'q huvb tiaj Jiu pun yem yia Eei puab Diaq mig a'q. maaib myenb heug yia taij huvb tiaj, mq paag yia Zxg lyrub meib Eei mcvg. yia kxvq, ‘yia maiq suv puad hxig yia Eei huvb tiaj weig zu'g huvb tiaj se zyruq xn taaib Eei myenb.’
24.22: Daa-witq zyrug hruq Jyenq lcvd waag pun sau-lo. sau-lo zyrug Rwrnj pyauq mig a'q. Daa-witq Zauj ninb Eei myenb faauj mivb yem nxm weib wrnq Eei txvj.
24.12: Toq zyruq yem huvb tiaj Zauj yia Bu'Dovj tunj sig. Toq zyruq weig yia winb pun meib, mq paag yia kanb Eei puad maiq zruj haiq Euvg hxig huvb tiaj.
24.15: weig naaiq Toq zyruq yem yia Zauj huvb tiaj Bu'Dovj zruj syemq zwid Jyen Tevj yia Bua tunj sig. Toq ninb zaab yaag Tevj yia zyrug Fruj yia pyauj Dutq meib Eei puab Diaq.”
24.13: Navq lob Nxi myenb maaib waab Pwij kxvq, ‘x'q sig mtaaib yem x'q myenb Zwrtq taaib.’ mq paag yia Eei puad maiq zruj haiq Euvg pun huvb tiaj.
24.1: sau-lo mivb zung fi-li-saa-tia myenb Rwrnj taaib, maaib myenb Buaj ninb, “Daa-witq yem en-ke-Di Eei teib puvb Waav.”

28.18: weig zu'g meib maiq mwavj zyruq Eei waag. ninb Qiaj Jiad! haig aa-maa-lekq myenb. meib yaag maiq ei ninb hatg Eei waag myetg ninb Bua. weig naaiq ib Nxi zyruq Zivj taaib Navq naaiq nx zruj pun meib.
28.8: sau-lo yeng ninb Eei lwib hruj zxv penj kanb taub zyrug Zauj i taub mJavg txn luvb mwrnd zang mivb lxd uaq taub kaanq hei Eei msia'q txn. huvb tiaj kxvq, “Toq Tevj yia naaig taub taig mivb Eei myenb Eei wrnb. yia kxvq haiq taub Eei Buaj, meib heug uaq taub Zwrtq taaib og.”
28.3: saa-mu-en kwei seij mig a'q. i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb weig ninb Raub Eyemq yaag txb ninb mivb zavj Jyenq ninb kanb Eei pwrnb muvq, laa-maa. sau-lo zung Zwrtq Revg kaanq hei myenb Zauj Bruq kwaaj Eei myenb, maiq pun yem teib puv.
28.21: uaq taub msia'q txn mivb Tauj sau-lo uaq, pwatg ninb za'kevb! kamb Riaj haig. uaq taub msia'q txn zyrug kxvq, “yia, meib Eei msia'q pru, maiq lovg mcvg Eei ei Jyenq meib Eei waag zruj.
28.14: sau-lo naaig uaq taub msia'q txn, “pwatg ninb Eei favj zeiq Navq haiq nx?” uaq taub msia'q txn tau, “maaib taub myenb koj myenb zu'q Jyenq tomb lwib Daauq Zwrtq taaib” sau-lo zyrug hiuq tu'q se saa-mu-en. sau-lo zyrug Baapq Fiag Dau paaij.
28.23: sau-lo maiq Kavq. ninb kxvq, “yia maiq Eang.” mq paag ninb Eei pru Zauj uaq taub msia'q txn Kwinj ninb. ninb zyrug mwavj ninb Bua Eei waag, yem ka'Diaq Dau Jiad sin taaib zweid Jyenq Zruj.
28.6: sau-lo naaig zyruq mq paag zyruq maiq tau ninb, maiq poj Beij pun ninb, yaag maiq lovg u-lim fai trug waag myenb tau.
28.2: Daa-witq tau aa-Kitq, “lovj a'q. meib zyrug hiuq tu'q yia meib Eei pru, haib zruj tu'q haiq Euvg.” aa-Kitq kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “lovj Eei. yia xij xn meib yetg liud zruj yia Eei sinb Len myenb.”
28.20: sau-lo haid saa-mu-en Navq naaiq nx kxvq, zyrug lyemb zeib hc'q ninb kamb Riaj haig, Kiv Fiag Dau mivb. ninb mau haig, maiq maaib yetg teij Qa'q, weig zu'g tu'q yetg Nxi Zauj yetg mwrnd ninb maiq Eang haiq Euvg.
28.24: uaq taub msia'q txn maaib taub vovb txn Jung yem uaq pyauq zyrug syepg syepq Eei taij taaib. ninb yaag zx'q Bwrnq Zaij taaib zruj maiq an pivq Eei Fuaq zi'q zyavj.
28.7: sau-lo kxvq Buaj ninb Eei pru, “Toq lxd taub kaanq hei Eei msia'q txn, weig pun yia tu'q mivb naaig ninb.” sau-lo Eei pru tau, “yem en-Do laavd maaib taub kaanq hei Eei msia'q txn.”
28.19: maiq taan Bua'g naaiq. zyruq xij zx'q i-saa-laa-en Zauj Jyenq meib Jiu pun yem fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei puab Diaq. Fav Nxi meib kanb Zauj meib Eei txn Bua zyrug Zauj yia yem naaiq. zyruq yaag xij zx'q i-saa-laa-en Eei Junb pcv Jiu pun yem fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei puab Diaq.”
28.17: zyruq zruj pun meib Navq ninb lovg yia kxvq Buaj meib nx. zyruq zuvq Zaavq meib Eei kua'q mivb Jiu pun Daa-witq mig a'q,
28.11: uaq taub msia'q txn naaig, “meib xij yia heug haiq taub Zwrtq taaib?” sau-lo tau, “Tevj yia heug saa-mu-en Zwrtq taaib.”
28.5: sau-lo mavg pwatg fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei Junb pcv kwanb zyrug hc'q ninb kamb Riaj haig. ninb Eei Hruq yaag lung Revg.
28.9: uaq taub msia'q txn kxvq Buaj huvb tiaj, “meib zuvq hiuq tu'q sau-lo Navq haiq nx zruj. ninb Pai kwavg yem teib puv Eei kaanq hei Eei myenb Zauj Bruq kwaaj Eei myenb, maiq pun ninb Bua yem teib puv. uaq Euvg meib weig haiq tiug taaib Duaq yia, Navq zcv Kruj Lopq xij zx'q yia Eei mcvg?”
28.16: saa-mu-en tau, “meib weig haiq tiug naaig yia? weig zu'g zyruq kwavg, maiq mavg meib yaag penj meib Eei winb wavq mig a'q.
28.4: fi-li-saa-tia myenb kapq zunq taaib lyepg Zyavq yem su-nem. sau-lo yaag heug i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb kapq zunq taaib zyrug lyepg Zyavq yem kin-Bo-aa Bov.
28.10: sau-lo zyavq Jyenq zyruq hruq waag kxvq Buaj uaq taub msia'q txn, “yia zyavq Jyenq zyavb Jyenq Eei zyruq lcvd meib zuvq maiq zu'g weig naaiq teij sig tivg zwid.”
28.22: ib zang Toq meib mwavj yia, meib Eei msia'q pru, Eei waag. Toq pun yia Beng ti'q tyen ka'naaiq pun meib Eang. weig pun meib haib maaib Qa'q Zwrtq Jauq.”
28.12: uaq taub msia'q txn yetq pwatg saa-mu-en, ninb zyrug heug Qiaj Bwi! Eei. ninb kxvq sau-lo, “meib weig haiq tiug Duaq yia? meib se sau-lo huvb.”
28.15: saa-mu-en naaig sau-lo, “meib la'Eauq yia, heug yia Zwrtq taaib zruj haiq Euvg?” sau-lo tau, “yia maaib Kwrnj Hruq Eei sig Niaq haig, weig zu'g fi-li-saa-tia myenb taaib xij Zauj yia Bx'q Jaaj. Tinb huvb yaag kwavg maiq mavg yia, maiq tau yia tauj kauj Eei waag. ninb maiq lovg trug waag myenb fai Beij Eei Beij tau yia. weig naaiq yia Zivj taaib heug meib Zwrtq taaib Buaj yia, yia yaag xij zu'g Navq haiq nx zruj?”
28.13: sau-lo kxvq Buaj ninb, “maiq tuvq kamb Riaj og. meib pwatg haiq Euvg?” uaq taub msia'q txn tau sau-lo, “yia pwatg taub zyenb yem Daub Diaq Zwrtq taaib.”
28.1: uaq teij zyavb hog. fi-li-saa-tia myenb kapq zunq xij mivb Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb Bx'q Jaaj. aa-Kitq kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “meib xij zu'g pia'g Hruq, meib Zauj kan meib Eei myenb xij zu'g Zauj Jyenq yia Zwrtq mivb Bx'q Jaaj.”
28.25: ninb zyrug txb taaib Beng pun sau-lo Zauj ninb Eei pru Bua Eang. ninb Bua Eang liud, tovb naaig mwrnd ninb Bua zyrug mivb mig a'q.

7.3: saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj i-saa-laa-en Eei yetg zuvq zeib fun, “sij kxvq meib Bua lovg Revg Hruq xij Rwrnj taaib lxd zyruq nx, xij zu'g kwavg Gxi kanb fivj myenb Eei zyenb. yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj yaag xij zu'g zx'q Gxi atg-Taa-lotq zyenb, zunq tivg Hruq lxd zyruq, Kuvj fub suj ninb kanb Navq. ninb zyrug Tevj meib Bua pyauj Dutq fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei puab Diaq.”
7.8: i-saa-laa-en myenb kxvq Buaj saa-mu-en, “Toq meib maiq tivb lyrub Eei weig yia Bua heug Jyenq Jrub zyruq, yia Bua Eei Tinb huvb, yaag Toq ninb Tevj yia Bua pyauj Dutq fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei puab Diaq.”
7.9: saa-mu-en zyrug zx'q taub maiq kcvb kwavg Exj Eei pa'ki yuvb txn zyavb taub puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq. saa-mu-en zyrug weig i-saa-laa-en myenb heug Jyenq Toq zyruq.  zyruq yaag tau ninb.
7.7: fi-li-saa-tia myenb haid kxvq i-saa-laa-en myenb kapq zunq yem mitq-paa. fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq zyrug Zwrtq mivb Bx'q i-saa-laa-en myenb. i-saa-laa-en myenb mwavj haid Navq naaig zyrug kamb Riaj haig fi-li-saa-tia myenb.
7.5: saa-mu-en cvj kxvq, “heug i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb kapq zunq yem mitq-paa muvq. yia zyrug weig meib Bua tauj kauj Toq zyruq. ”
7.16: Havb Havj ninb Zwrtq mivb yrub Jyenq Betg-en, kin-kaan Zauj mitq-paa muvq, yaag yem naaiq teij nxmb nxm txvj Tevj i-saa-laa-en myenb tunj sig.
7.17: Ga'haaq ninb Rwrnj laa-maa zivb weig zu'g ninb Eei pyauq yem uaq. yem naaig ninb yaag Tevj i-saa-laa-en myenb tunj sig. saa-mu-en yaag yem uaq weig zyruq Zeij nxm ziab txvb.
7.14: tovb fi-li-saa-tia myenb Zaavq i-saa-laa-en myenb uaq teij zivb yem e-Ko-lon mivb Tauj katg zivb, i-saa-laa-en myenb cvj tu'q Rwrnj Revg taaib. naaiq teij zivb weib kxmj Eei teig, i-saa-laa-en myenb yaag Fruj Zwrtq, maiq zu'g yem fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei puab Diaq. uaq zang i-saa-laa-en myenb Zauj aa-mo-lai myenb yaag Taaib pcvb Eei yem.
7.4: i-saa-laa-en myenb zyrug kwavg Baa-an zyenb Zauj atg-Taa-lotq zyenb, Kuvj fub suj zyruq Navq.
7.2: lcvd vcvg waag faav yem Ki-li-yaatq-ye-aa-lim laub haig, zuvq pwavq Eig zyepg Havj mig a'q. i-saa-laa-en Eei yetg zuvq zeib fun zyrug Namb Rwrnj lxd zyruq.
7.6: ninb Bua zyrug kapq zunq yem mitq-paa, yaag Damq uam taaib yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen toj Zwrtq fuvj pun zyruq. uaq Nxi ninb Bua zei maiq Eang haiq Euvg. yem naaig ninb Bua kxvq, “yia Bua paamd zwid txvg zyruq. ” saa-mu-en zyrug yem mitq-paa Tevj i-saa-laa-en myenb tunj sig.
7.13: Navq naaig fi-li-saa-tia myenb zu'g swei ninb Bua yaag maiq cvj pia'g i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei teig a'q. yem saa-mu-en Eei seij zeiq zyruq tavq Jyenq fi-li-saa-tia myenb.
7.12: saa-mu-en zyrug zx'q nxm la'pyeiq lyepg Jiad taaib yem mitq-paa muvq Zauj sen Bu'Dovj, yaag Zwrtq la'pyeiq Eei Buaj heug e-Ben-e-se, weig zu'g ninb kxvq, “zyruq Tevj Bua Tauj ib zang.”
7.15: saa-mu-en zyavb seij Tevj i-saa-laa-en myenb tunj sig.
7.11: i-saa-laa-en myenb yem mitq-paa Zwrtq mivb zung fi-li-saa-tia myenb, taij Jyenq ninb Bua mivb Tauj Betg-Kaa.
7.1: Ki-li-yaatq-ye-aa-lim myenb zyrug taaib txb zyruq Eei faav mivb Tauj aa-Bi-naa-Dapg Eei pyauq. ninb Eei pyauq yem nxm Bovb aiq kub vwaaig. ninb Bua yaag saaj aa-Bi-naa-Dapg Eei txn, e-le-aa-saa, Zivb Revg taaib, pun ninb kruj zyruq Eei faav.
7.10: saa-mu-en fovg hxg puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq uaq zang, fi-li-saa-tia myenb taaib fatq, xij Bx'q i-saa-laa-en myenb. mq paag uaq Nxi zyruq pun pxvd tomb Ba'ov Bwi, hc'q fi-li-saa-tia myenb lung Revg zyrug swei i-saa-laa-en myenb mig a'q.

29.3: fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei tomb pcvb pyeiq kxvq, “naaiq teij hipq-lu myenb taaib naaiq zruj haiq Euvg?” aa-Kitq tau fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei tomb pcvb pyeiq, “naaiq taub se i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei huvb tiaj, sau-lo, Eei Jyen, Daa-witq, maiq zeid? ninb taaib Zauj Bua yem tu'q Zamb Nxi Zamb Havj a'q. yem ninb pyauj taaib lxd yia Tauj ib Nxi, yia maiq pwatg ninb zruj txvg Jiaj haiq Euvg.”
29.8: Daa-witq kxvq Buaj aa-Kitq, “yia zruj txvg haiq Euvg? yem yia taaib lxd meib Tauj ib zang meib pwatg yia txvg Jiaj haiq Euvg fai? yia weig haiq tiug maiq tu'q mivb Bx'q yia Eei zyruq, huvb tiaj, Eei winb wavq?”
29.4: mq paag fi-li-saa-tia Eei pcvb pyeiq Qiaj Jiad haig aa-Kitq zyrug kxvq Buaj ninb, “Toq meib heug naaiq taub myenb Rwrnj mivb, pun ninb Rwrnj tovb meib tivg zyavj pun ninb yem Eei txvj. maiq tuvq pun ninb Zauj yia Bua Zwrtq mivb Bx'q Jaaj. Raub heij Bua Bx'q Jyenq Jaaj Eei zyavb hog, ninb Byenq Hruq penj Bua Eei winb wavq. naaiq taub myenb haib lovg haiq Euvg za'eij Zauj ninb Eei zyruq hxpg taaib? ninb maiq zeid zx'q yem naaiq Eei myenb Eei mGxvq fai?
29.2: fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq Zwrtq mivb. ninb Bua Eei Junb pcv kan Jyenq mivb penj yetg kwanb yetg kwanb Eei. maaib teij yetg pc'q taub, maaib teij yetg Zin taub. Daa-witq Zauj kan ninb Eei myenb Zauj aa-Kitq kan Jyenq ninb Bua Eei Ga'haaq Gaav mivb.
29.6: aa-Kitq zyrug heug Daa-witq taaib kxvq Buaj ninb, “yia zyavq Jyenq zyavb Jyenq Eei zyruq lcvd waag. meib zruj Hruq zivj Eei myenb. yia kanb nx, a'Neiq pun meib Zauj Jyenq yia mivb Bx'q Jaaj. yem meib taaib Zauj yia yem uaq Nxi Tauj ib zang, yia maiq pwatg meib txvg Jiaj haiq Euvg. mq paag zwavj pyeiq zeiq maiq a'Neiq meib.
29.9: aa-Kitq tau Daa-witq, “yia hiuq tu'q ei yia kanb Eei mziv mavg nx, meib hxpg yia Eei Hruq haig Navq Tinb huvb Eei finb myenb nx. mq paag fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei tomb pcvb pyeiq kxvq, ‘maiq tuvq pun ninb Zauj yia Bua mivb Bx'q Jaaj.’
29.11: Daa-witq Zauj kan ninb Eei myenb zyrug luvb Dxm Ryruq Eei Jiad sin taaib Rwrnj fi-li-saa-tia teib puv. mq paag fi-li-saa-tia myenb mivb yitq-le-en mig a'q.
29.5: ninb Bua Zavj heij paauj Ruv kxvq, ‘sau-lo taij myenb penj Zinb Zin, Daa-witq taij myenb penj waanb waang’ se maiq zeid naaiq taub Daa-witq fai?”
29.7: weig naaiq Toq meib Rwrnj a'q, pcvb xn Eei mivb maa'b! Navq naaig meib zyrug maiq zu'g fi-li-saa-tia myenb maiq a'Neiq meib.”
29.1: fi-li-saa-tia myenb tiug Rxib ninb Bua Eei yetg zuvq pcv yem aa-fekq. i-saa-laa-en myenb lyepg Zyavq yem yitq-le-en uamb zivq ka'Len.
29.10: Navq naaig, meib Zauj meib Eei zyruq Eei pru, tovb kan meib Eei myenb, Fav Dxm Jiad sin Ryruq Eei, zuaq Jyenq luvb yetq Fav zyrug Zwrtq Jauq mivb a'q.”

19.18: Daa-witq zyrug pyauj Dutq mig a'q. ninb mivb laa-maa zivb lxd saa-mu-en, yaag zx'q sau-lo zruj pun ninb Eei yetg zuvq Jauq kxvq pun saa-mu-en mwavj. ninb Zauj saa-mu-en zyrug mivb yem naa-yotq.
19.8: Ga'haaq cvj maaib Bx'q Jaaj Eei sig. Daa-witq zyrug Zwrtq mivb Zauj fi-li-saa-tia myenb Bx'q Jaaj, yaag taij fi-li-saa-tia myenb taig Zamq! haig. fi-li-saa-tia myenb zyrug yem ninb Eei uaq Daavg mcvj pyauj.
19.3: meib pivj haiq Ropq lomb Waav, yia xij mivb uaq sruq Jyenq yia Eei tia Eei ka'Len kxvq meib Eei Jauq pun yia Eei tia mwavj. yia hiuq tu'q meib Eei Jauq Navq haiq nx, yia zyrug Buaj meib.”
19.21: maaib myenb txb naaiq teij sig mivb Buaj sau-lo. ninb zyrug cvj Paaiq teij myenb mivb. uaq teij myenb yaag Zauj Jyenq trug Tinb huvb Eei waag. sau-lo cvj Paaiq ta'faam Rung myenb mivb. uaq teij yaag fib Navq Eei trug Tinb huvb Eei waag.
19.14: sau-lo Paaiq myenb mivb zx'q Daa-witq uaq zang mi-Kaan kxvq, “Daa-witq maiq lovj.”
19.23: sau-lo zyrug mivb laa-maa zivb, naa-yotq uaq. Tinb huvb Eei sivj livb Fiag taaib yem Jyenq sau-lo. ninb zyrug yetg ping mivb, yetg ping trug Tinb huvb Eei waag, Tauj laa-maa zivb, naa-yotq uaq.
19.6: sau-lo zyrug mwavj yo-naa-Taan Eei waag. sau-lo hruq Jyenq waag kxvq, “yia zyavq Jyenq zyavb Jyenq Eei zyruq lcvd waag, Daa-witq zuvq maiq zu'g taij taig a'q.”
19.2: yo-naa-Taan zyrug kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “yia Eei tia, sau-lo, lxd Qavj taij meib. weig naaiq, Fav Nxi Dxm meib xij zu'g faij fim, xij zu'g lxd txvj pivj Jyenq Bweid Eei.
19.20: sau-lo zyrug Paaiq myenb mivb zx'q Daa-witq. mivb Eei myenb pwatg kwanb trug waag myenb yem uaq trug Tinb huvb Eei waag, saa-mu-en zruj pyeiq zeiq sruq Jyenq txb ninb Bua. Tinb huvb Eei sivj livb Fiag taaib yem Jyenq sau-lo Paaiq mivb Eei myenb, ninb Bua zyrug Zauj Jyenq trug waag.
19.24: ninb yaag Jaiq Gxi lwib hruj txv Jyenq saa-mu-en trug Tinb huvb Eei waag, cvj lcvb kcvq Eei pweij yetg Nxi, yetg mwrnd. weig naaig myenb Zivj taaib kxvq, “sau-lo yaag penj taub trug waag myenb fai?”
19.7: yo-naa-Taan zyrug heug Daa-witq, yaag zx'q naaiq teij yetg zuvq sig kxvq Buaj ninb. yo-naa-Taan yaag txb Daa-witq mivb sau-lo uaq. Daa-witq zyrug yem sau-lo Eei Ra'Myen Navq zinb Daavg nx.
19.19: maaib myenb mivb kxvq Buaj sau-lo, “Daa-witq mivb yem laa-maa zivb, naa-yotq uaq nxm txvj.”
19.17: sau-lo kxvq mi-Kaan, “meib weig haiq tiug Navq naaiq Duaq yia, puvj yia Eei winb wavq pyauj mivb, ninb zyrug pyauj Dutq mig a'q.” mi-Kaan tau sau-lo, “ninb kxvq Buaj yia, ‘puvj yia mivb maa'b! xij pun yia taij meib zruj haiq Euvg?’+”
19.11: sau-lo Paaiq myenb mivb Daa-witq Eei pyauq Zyenb mavg, zuaq Tauj luvb Fav taij ninb a'q. mq paag Daa-witq Eei auq, mi-Kaan, kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “sij kxvq ib mwrnd meib maiq pyauj mcvg nx, Fav Nxi meib zuvq xij zu'g taij taig a'q.”
19.5: ninb maiq lovg mcvg Eei mivb taij uaq taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb. zyruq Tevj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb tu'q hivb Jiaj. uaq zang aa tia pwatg yaag a'Neiq haig. ib zang weig haiq tiug xij zruj zwid taij Daa-witq pun maiq zruj txvg Eei myenb Eei Ryaamq lyrug Zwrtq yaag maiq maaib kxnb pcvj.”
19.9: yem zyruq taaib Eei x'q myenq cvj taaib mxb sau-lo mig a'q. uaq zang sau-lo yem ninb Eei ting nanq Jyenq Zav. Daa-witq yaag Patq taanb paab pun ninb mwavj.
19.16: Paaiq mivb Eei myenb pia'g mivb, pwatg miub favj yem uaq Zruj, yaag maaib yuvb pyei Eei Romb taub yem mGxvq.
19.4: yo-naa-Taan Zev Daa-witq pun ninb Eei tia mwavj. ninb kxvq, “Toq aa tia maiq tuvq zruj zwid hxig meib Eei pru, Daa-witq, weig zu'g Daa-witq maiq zruj haiq Euvg zwid txvg aa tia. ninb zruj Eei Euvb Euvg yaag Tevj tu'q tia Zamq haig.
19.10: sau-lo piu Zav mivb xij Ropq Daa-witq pavg Fovg tiv Jyenq, mq paag Daa-witq simq Dutq mig a'q. Zav zyrug tiv Jyenq uaq Fovg. uaq mwrnd Daa-witq pyauj Dutq mig a'q.
19.22: sau-lo kanb zyrug mivb laa-maa zivb. taaib Tauj sej-Ku muvq Eei tomb uamb Kwrtq ka'Len ninb naaig myenb, “saa-mu-en Zauj Daa-witq yem haaij?” maaib myenb tau ninb, “ninb Bua i taub yem laa-maa zivb ka'Euad, naa-yotq uaq nxm txvj.”
19.12: mi-Kaan zyrug puvj Daa-witq yavb fov mwrnb Fiag. Daa-witq zyrug pyauj Dutq mig a'q.
19.15: sau-lo cvj Paaiq myenb mivb mavg Daa-witq, yaag kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “lyemb Zruj kcv Jyenq ninb taaib yia naaiq, weig pun yia taij ninb a'q.”
19.13: mi-Kaan cvj zx'q miub favj an Jyenq Zruj, zx'q lovg yuvb pyei zruj taaib Eei Romb taub pun Romd Jyenq, yaag zx'q lwi homg Jyenq.
19.1: sau-lo heug ninb Eei txn, yo-naa-Taan, Zauj ninb Eei zwavj pru, taij Daa-witq. mq paag sau-lo Eei txn, yo-naa-Taan, Namq haig Daa-witq.

17.18: yaag zx'q naaiq teij zyepg Dunb Exb Mei vcvg txb mivb pun kunq yetg Zin taub pcv Eei pcvb pyeiq. mavg kaaj meib Eei kxj Bua yem lovj Eei fai? yaag zx'q teij ninb Bua Eei ka'naaiq txb Rwrnj taaib.
17.45: Daa-witq yaag kxvq Buaj uaq taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb, “meib nanq Ru'g Daauq, nanq Zav Zauj piu Eei Zav taaib Zauj yia Bx'q Jaaj, mq paag yia tevq nrnb Jiaj Eei zyruq Eei Buaj taaib, se i-saa-laa-en Junb pcv Eei Tinb huvb, tovb meib Druq uaq taub.
17.3: fi-li-saa-tia myenb sruq Jyenq uaq nxm zxv, i-saa-laa-en myenb sruq Jyenq naaiq nxm zxv. Bu'Dovj maaib nxm hxvd Gc'q Jyenq.
17.43: uaq taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb zyrug naaig Daa-witq, “yia zruj Juq meib Zivj taaib txb Jyenq pyaab Byaag taaib Bx'q yia fai?” uaq taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb zyrug tevq ninb Eei zyenb Eei Buaj zyruj Daa-witq.
17.50: Navq naaig Daa-witq lovg tiub Dopg Laav Zauj nxm la'pyeiq hivb Jiaj uaq taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb, pun ninb ta'Gopq Kiv Fiag Dau taig. Daa-witq maiq maaib Ru'g Daauq yem ninb Eei puad.
17.14: Daa-witq penj txnb laai. uaq teij pua taub tomb kxj kan sau-lo mivb mig a'q.
17.48: uaq taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb kunq zruj kunq taaib fatq Daa-witq, Daa-witq syepg syepq Eei Tiuj mivb Tauj Bx'q Jaaj Eei txvj xij Zauj ninb Bx'q Jaaj.
17.34: mq paag Daa-witq kxvq Buaj sau-lo, “yia, meib Eei pru, Tevj yia Eei tia kruj yia Eei tia Eei pa'ki yuvb. haiq zang maaib syenb fai Jyepq taaib vaatg pa'ki yuvb txn Tx mivb,
17.2: sau-lo Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb kapq zunq yem e-laa hxvd lyepg Zyavq. ninb Bua ziuj Bx'q Jaaj Eei yetg Eeig Baib Jyenq xij Zauj fi-li-saa-tia myenb Bx'q Jaaj.
17.36: yia, meib Eei pru, taij taig syenb Zauj Jyepq mig a'q. naaiq taub maiq Jiaj kaatq Eei leid Eei fi-li-saa-tia myenb yaag xij zu'g Navq taub uaq teij Yiab zxib nx, weig zu'g ninb Druq zyavb Jyenq Eei Tinb huvb Eei Junb pcv.”
17.35: yia zyrug zung zaaig Bx'q ninb yaag zx'q yem ninb Eei Rwib pcvj Eei pa'ki yuvb txn Rwrnj taaib. sij kxvq ninb Jiad sin taaib Zauj yia pxvd nx, yia zyrug Eau Jyenq ninb Eei Jaavb Diaq Bx'q ninb taig mig a'q.
17.24: i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb pwatg uaq taub myenb, ninb Bua kamb Riaj kau, zyrug Tiuj pyauj.
17.7: Zavb pcvj Daauq Eei Navq Datq Dia Eei Dyavj nx, lovg Lia'q zcvj Jyenq tweib mweid, Niab taaub leib maiq ko pyei Jxib zyepg feij luvd. Tevj ninb nanq Txvb paaib uaq taub pcv Zwrtq mivb Daavg.
17.17: maaib Nxi Jyetg-si kxvq Buaj ninb Eei txn, Daa-witq, “zx'q naaiq Tovq Zaauq taaib Eei Meiq Zauj zyepg nxm Fuaq, syepg syepq Eei txb mivb uaq Zyavq pun meib Eei kxj Bua.
17.58: sau-lo naaig ninb, “meib naaiq taub myenb lunj myenb aa'b! meib haiq taub Eei txn?” Daa-witq tau, “yia se meib Eei pru, Betg-le-hem myenb, Jyetg-si Eei txn.”
17.49: Daa-witq lovg ninb Eei puad lom pia'g Bua'g Jxvj mivb, zx'q tu'q nxm la'pyeiq Zwrtq taaib Yetq Jyenq Dopg Laav fevj mivb Bx'q uaq taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei pyxvb. la'pyeiq pia'g mwrtq ka'Euad mivb, ninb zyrug ta'Gopq Kiv Fiag Dau.
17.11: sau-lo Zauj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb haid liud uaq taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei waag, ninb Bua kamb Riaj kau, Ba'Riu xij yu'g Revg a'q.
17.33: sau-lo kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “meib maiq haib mivb Zauj uaq taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb Bx'q Jaaj lx'g, weig zu'g meib Zxg penj txnb lunj. uaq taub myenb yem faij Eei zyavb hog ho'g Bx'q Jaaj taaib Tauj ib zang a'q.”

17.40: ninb zyrug nanq Jyenq ninb Eei pyaab Byaag mivb uaq Do'g Len kinq tu'q pyaa nxm Lyruq Fav Eei la'pyeiq taaib tapq Jyenq ninb pwij mivb kruj pa'ki yuvb Eei Bua'g Jxvj. puad nanq Jyenq fevj la'pyeiq Eei Dopg Laav. ninb zyrug mivb nitq fatq uaq taub fi-li-saa-tia myenb.
