30.4: Daa-witq Zauj Jyenq ninb Eei pc'g fivj Eyemq Qiaj Bwi haig. ninb Bua Eyemq kau lyemb maiq maaib Qa'q a'q.
30.10: mq paag Daa-witq kanb Zauj feij pc'q taub myenb zung Jyenq aa-maa-lekq myenb mivb. maaib Eig pc'q taub myenb mau haig, Jiaj maiq tu'q Be-soj Do'q, zyrug tivb Jyenq uaq.
30.22: kan Daa-witq mivb Eei myenb maaib teij x'q myenb Zauj myenb waaig myenb kxvq, “naaiq teij myenb maiq kan Bua mivb. Bua Zaavq taaib Eei ka'naaiq Bua maiq pun ninb Bua. Kuvj pun kx'g myenb txb kx'g myenb Eei aub Jweiq mivb a'q.”
30.12: pun Kwaaiq vovb Exj pyruq Eei Fuaq ninb Eang Zauj i Dunb a'vung pyrub Gaai. ninb Eang liud zyrug henq Jiad taaib, weig zu'g ninb maiq tu'q Eang Naavj, maiq tu'q hopq uam tu'q pua Nxi pua mwrnd a'q.
30.15: Daa-witq naaig ninb, “meib haib txb yia Bua Fiag Tauj uaq kwanb pcv Eei fai?” ninb tau, “meib xij zu'g zyavq Jyenq Tinb huvb lcvd waag kxvq meib maiq taij yia yaag maiq zx'q yia Jiu pun yia Eei zyruq, yia zyrug txb meib mivb Tauj uaq kwanb za'g pcv.”
30.13: Daa-witq naaig ninb, “meib haiq taub Eei myenb yaag yem haiq Dau taaib?” ninb tau, “yia i-yipq myenb, zruj aa-maa-lekq myenb Eei nrub, tovb pua Nxi Jiaj taaib naaiq yia maiq lovj. yia Eei zyruq kwavg Jyenq yia mivb mig a'q.
30.1: Ga'haaq Tauj ta'faam Nxi, Daa-witq Zauj Jyenq ninb Eei myenb taaib Tauj sikg-laakq zivb, aa-maa-lekq myenb zuvq taaib luq ne-kepg yaag luq sikg-laakq mig a'q. ninb Bua Bx'q hivb sikg-laakq, yaag lovg trud puaq Qwi Revg.
30.26: Daa-witq Rwrnj Tauj sikg-laakq zivb, ninb zx'q teij Zaavq tu'q taaib Eei ka'naaiq fuvj pun ninb Eei txig, se tovb yu-Daa teib puv Eei myenb koj. ninb kxvq, “yia zx'q naaiq teij zivb Eeig fuvj pun meib Bua, se yem zyruq Eei winb wavq Zaavq tu'q taaib Eei ka'naaiq.”
30.25: yem naaig taaib, Daa-witq zyrug lyepg naaiq tiug leib fivj penj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei leib latg Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi.

27.3: Daa-witq Zauj kan ninb Eei yetg zuvq myenb mivb yem katg zivb, aa-Kitq huvb uaq. kx'g myenb txb Jyenq kx'g myenb Eei Mwavq txig mivb. Daa-witq yaag txb ninb Eei i taub auq, se yitq-le-en myenb, aa-hi-no-am, Zauj naa-Baan Eei aub kwaaq, Kaan-men myenb, aa-Bi-kaa-yin.
27.8: Daa-witq Zauj kan ninb Eei myenb faauj mivb luq ke-su myenb, ke-se myenb Zauj aa-maa-lekq myenb, weig zu'g yem lob Nxi taaib naaiq teij myenb mtaaib yem uaq nxm teib puv, se yem ko Tauj su-waa muvq cvj mivb Tauj i-yipq teib puv.
27.9: Daa-witq Bx'q uaq nxm teib puv, maiq kunq mJavg msia'q, ninb maiq lyrub yetg taub. ninb Bua luq Revg pa'ki yuvb, vovb, lxb, lxb Txb, Zauj lwib hruj, Ga'haaq Rwrnj aa-Kitq uaq.
27.7: Daa-witq pia'g mivb yem fi-li-saa-tia teib puv yetg Havj Zauj pyei Laaj Eia'g.
27.5: Daa-witq kxvq Buaj aa-Kitq, “sij kxvq yia hxpg huvb tiaj Eei Hruq nx, Toq Paaiq nxm muvq pun yia yem uaq. yia, meib Eei pru, weig haiq tiug xij zu'g Zauj huvb tiaj yem tomb zivb ka'Euad?”
27.4: maaib myenb mivb kxvq Buaj sau-lo, Daa-witq pyauj mivb yem katg muvq mig a'q. sau-lo zyrug kwavg maiq lxd Daa-witq.
27.2: Daa-witq Zauj Jyenq kan ninb uaq teij lua'g pc'q taub myenb zyrug mivb lxd katg muvq Eei huvb tiaj, maa-okg Eei txn, aa-Kitq.
27.6: uaq Nxi aa-Kitq zyrug zx'q sikg-laakq zivb Jiu pun Daa-witq. sikg-laakq zivb zyrug kwei yu-Daa huvb Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi.
27.12: aa-Kitq puvj Hruq Daa-witq. ninb yem Hruq Namq, “ninb zruj pun ninb Jwavg fivj Eei i-saa-laa-en myenb Rxv haig ninb. Navq naaig ninb zyrug yetg liud zruj yia Eei pru a'q.”
27.11: Daa-witq maiq lyrub yetg taub mJavg msia'q tu'q Zwrtq sivj mcvg, haib txb fyenj mivb uaq katg zivb. ninb yem Hruq Namq, “Riaj ninb Bua haib zx'q yia Bua zruj Eei sig kxvq Buaj myenb cvj kxvq Daa-witq Navq naaiq Navq uaq zruj.” naaiq se Daa-witq yem fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei teib puv Eei zyavb hog zruj Eei sig.
27.1: Daa-witq yem Hruq Namq, “maaib nxm Nxi yia zuvq xij zu'g sau-lo taij yia a'q. yia pyauj mivb yem fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei teib puv kaub lovj Jiaj. sau-lo zyrug maiq yem i-saa-laa-en teib puv ka'Euad zung yia, yia zyrug haib pyauj Dutq sau-lo Eei puab Diaq.”
27.10: aa-Kitq haiq zang naaig, “ib Nxi meib mivb luq haiq nxm teib puv taaib?” Daa-witq tau, “mivb luq yu-Daa teib puv Eei naamb puv,” fai “mivb luq ye-laa-me-en myenb Eei naamb puv,” fai “mivb luq Ke-nai myenb Eei naamb puv.”

11.3: yaa-Betg muvq Eei myenb koj kxvq Buaj naa-haatg, “Toq meib pun zyavb hog yia Bua siag Nxi. zuaq yia Paaiq trug fyenj myenb mivb kxmj i-saa-laa-en teig. sij kxvq maiq maaib haiq taub haib Fruj tu'q yia Bua nx, yia Bua zyrug lcvd Zwrtq taaib Eyemg mau pun meib.”
11.8: sau-lo yem Be-sekq tiug Rxib pcv. i-saa-laa-en Eei pcv yetg zuvq maaib faab zyepg waang taub, yu-Daa Eei pcv maaib pua waang taub.
11.9: ninb Bua zyrug kxvq Buaj uaq teij trug fyenj myenb, “meib Bua xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx kxvq Buaj yaa-Betg-ki-le-aatg myenb. Fav Nxi, Eutg to'g Eei zyavb hog, meib Bua zyrug tu'q Fruj a'q.” trug fyenj myenb Rwrnj mivb kxvq Buaj yaa-Betg myenb uaq zang, ninb Bua za'kevb a'Neiq haig a'q.
11.7: ninb zyrug zx'q yetg txij vovb taaib Va'q penj ziaj teij pun trug fyenj myenb txb mivb kxmj i-saa-laa-en teig yaag kxvq, “haiq taub maiq Zwrtq taaib kan sau-lo Zauj saa-mu-en nx, xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx zruj pun uaq taub Eei vovb.” zyruq pun pc'g fivj kamb Riaj haig. ninb Bua zyrug tovb tiug Hruq Zwrtq taaib.
11.5: uaq zang sau-lo Javb Jav yem Deig hxvb Jyenq vovb Rwrnj taaib. sau-lo zyrug naaig ninb Bua, “pc'g fivj zruj haiq Euvg Qa'q Eyemq?” ninb Bua zyrug zx'q yaa-Betg myenb Eei Jaub lrug kxvq pun ninb mwavj.
11.14: saa-mu-en zyrug kxvq Buaj zwavj pc'g fivj, “taaib maa'b! Bua lomb Rxib mivb kin-kaan, yem uaq syavb lyepg Jiad sau-lo zruj Bua Eei huvb.”
11.4: trug fyenj myenb mivb Tauj sau-lo yem Eei ki-Be-aa zivb, zx'q naaiq teij Jaub lrug kxvq pun pc'g fivj mwavj. yetg zuvq pc'g fivj zyrug puvb siv puvb Qiaj Eyemq tu'q Bwi haig.
11.2: mq paag am-mon myenb, naa-haatg, kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “yia Zauj meib Bua lyepg Jiad vcvg waag tu'q Eei, mq paag meib Bua xij zu'g lcvd yetg Euvg Daavg. yia xij kweij Zwrtq meib Bua taub taub myenb Eei Byaaug mcvj mziv, zruj pun i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb zu'g Eaiq.”
11.6: sau-lo haid naaiq teij fyenj, Tinb huvb Eei sivj livb Zamb Zamq Eei taaib yem Jyenq ninb. sau-lo za'kevb Qiaj Jiad haig.
11.13: mq paag sau-lo kxvq, “ib Nxi maiq tuvq pun haiq taub zu'g taij taig, weig zu'g ib Nxi zyruq Fruj Bua i-saa-laa-en myenb.”
11.12: pc'g fivj zyrug kxvq Buaj saa-mu-en “kxvq, ‘sau-lo za'kevb xij kunq yia Bua fai?’ uaq teij myenb se haiq taub? zx'q ninb Bua Zwrtq taaib pun yia Bua taij kwavg mivb.”
11.15: yetg zuvq pc'g fivj zyrug mivb kin-kaan mig a'q. yem kin-kaan ninb Bua txv Jyenq zyruq lyepg sau-lo zruj huvb. ninb Bua yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen fovg hxg ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq. sau-lo Zauj zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug yem uaq za'kevb Fyenb yrub xnb lx'g haig.
11.11: ta'Eeig Nxi sau-lo zx'q pc'g fivj pun zruj pua kwanb. luvb Byrub Byrud Fav Eei zyavb hog ninb Bua pia'g am-mon myenb Eei Zyavq taij am-mon myenb Tauj Eutg to'g Eei zyavb hog. zevg Fiag tu'q mcvg Zwrtq uaq teij faatq Raanj Revg tov taub fai taub Eei pyauj, maiq maaib penj yetg txij a'q.
11.1: am-mon myenb Eei huvb, naa-haatg, mivb lyepg Zyavq weib kxmj xij Bx'q yaa-Betg-ki-le-aatg. yaa-Betg muvq Eei yetg zuvq pc'g fivj kxvq Buaj naa-haatg, “Toq Zauj yia Bua lyepg Jiad vcvg waag, yia Bua zyrug lcvd fub suj meib.”
11.10: yaa-Betg myenb zyrug kxvq Buaj am-mon myenb, “Fav Nxi yia Bua lcvd Zwrtq taaib Eyemg mau pun meib Bua. meib Bua kunq sweib eij zruj pun yia Bua ziuj meib Bua pwatg hxpg zu'g zruj.”

5.3: ta'Eeig Dxm atg-Dotg zivb Eei pc'g fivj Jiad sin Ryruq Eei mivb mavg, pwatg Daa-kon miub favj ta'Gopq Kiv Fiag Dau zyruq Eei faav Ra'Myen mcvj mivb. ninb Bua zyrug zx'q Daa-kon miub favj lyepg Jiad taaib an Jyenq ninb Eei lob txvj.
5.8: ninb Bua zyrug Paaiq myenb mivb heug fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei yetg zuvq pyeiq zeiq kapq zunq Zaavb laavb. ninb Bua naaig, “Bua xij zu'g Navq haiq nx zruj weig i-saa-laa-en Eei Tinb huvb Eei faav?” pyeiq zeiq Bua tau, “xij zu'g txb i-saa-laa-en Eei Tinb huvb Eei faav mivb katg zivb.” ninb Bua zyrug txb i-saa-laa-en Eei Tinb huvb Eei faav mivb an Jyenq uaq.
5.9: ninb Bua txb Tauj katg zivb uaq, Ga'haaq zyruq yaag tivg uaq nxm zivb Eei zwid, zruj pun uaq nxm zivb Eei myenb lung Revg. ninb pun zivb Eei myenb maiq kunq koj lunj, yetg zuvq zyavb ka'naaiq Revg.
5.7: atg-Dotg myenb pwatg naaiq teij sig Zwrtq, ninb Bua kxvq, “maiq tuvq pun i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei Tinb huvb Eei faav Zauj Bua yem naaiq a'q, weig zu'g ninb Niab Niaq Eei tivg Bua Eei zwid, yaag tivg Bua Eei Daa-kon zyenb Eei zwid.”
5.5: weig naaiq Daa-kon zyenb Eei sai myenb Zauj yetg zuvq pia'g Daa-kon miub pyauq Eei myenb Zivj taaib maiq Zaaiq atg-Dotg zivb, Daa-kon zyenb Eei miub pyauq Eei kcvb Bc'q Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi.
5.4: mq paag ta'Eeig Nxi ninb Bua Jiad sin Ryruq Eei mivb mavg, pwatg Daa-kon miub favj cvj ta'Gopq Kiv Fiag Dau, yem zyruq Eei faav Ra'Myen mcvj. mq paag Daa-kon Eei mGxvq Zauj i Jia'q puad nauq Dutq taaib yem Jyenq miub pyauq Eei kcvb Bc'q. Kuvj zevg ninb Eei sin Navq.
5.2: fi-li-saa-tia myenb zyrug txb Tinb huvb Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav pia'g Daa-kon zyenb Eei miub pyauq yaag an Jyenq Daa-kon Eei miub favj ka'Len.
5.6: zyruq Niab Niaq Eei tivg atg-Dotg zivb Zauj weib kxmj uaq teij myenb Eei zwid. ninb pun ninb Bua zu'g Kruq yaag zyavb to'g haig Eei zweib.
5.12: maiq taig uaq teij myenb zyavb zweib to'g. uaq nxm zivb Eei myenb heug Eei Qiaj zuvq faauj Tauj kub vwaaig luvb.
5.11: weig naaiq ninb Bua Paaiq myenb mivb heug fi-li-saa-tia Eei zwavj pyeiq zeiq taaib kapq zunq zyrug kxvq, “xij zu'g fuvj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei Tinb huvb Eei faav Rwrnj mivb an Jyenq ninb Eei lob txvj weig maiq pun uaq nxm faav taij Bua Zauj Bua Eei pc'g fivj.” weig zu'g kxmj uaq nxm zivb Eei myenb faanq lung, kamb Riaj taig. yem uaq Tinb huvb Niab Niaq Eei tivg ninb Bua Eei zwid.
5.1: fi-li-saa-tia myenb Zaavq tu'q Tinb huvb Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav, Ga'haaq ninb Bua yem e-Ben-e-se txb mivb Tauj atg-Dotg zivb.
5.10: ninb Bua zyrug fuvj Tinb huvb Eei faav mivb e-Ko-lon zivb. mq paag Tinb huvb Eei faav Tauj e-Ko-lon zivb uaq zang, e-Ko-lon Eei myenb heug Jyenq kxvq, “ninb Bua txb i-saa-laa-en Eei Tinb huvb Eei faav taaib xij taij yia Bua Zauj yia Bua Eei zwavj pc'g fivj.”

9.18: sau-lo mivb Tauj saa-mu-en Eei Ra'Myen, zivb kcvb uaq, naaig ninb, “Toq Buaj yia, hiuq tu'q zinb hod Eei sig uaq laanb myenb Eei pyauq yem haaij?”
9.8: ninb Eei pru tau sau-lo, “yia maaib nxm Eaanb levj yia xij pun Tinb huvb Eei myenb, Toq ninb Buaj Jauq Bua.”
9.3: sau-lo Eei tia, Kitq, Eei ziaj taub lxb Eeid tivj laaib mivb. Kitq zyrug kxvq Buaj ninb Eei txn, sau-lo, “txb yetg taub pru Zauj Jyenq meib mivb lxd uaq teij lxb maa'b!”
9.21: sau-lo tau, “yia Ben-yaa-min fivj Eei myenb, yem i-saa-laa-en Eei fivj ka'Euad kaub faij Jiaj Eei fivj maiq zeid? yem Ben-yaa-min fivj ka'Euad yia Eei puvb pwrng kaub faij Jiaj maiq zeid? meib weig haiq tiug Zauj yia Navq naaiq nx kxvq?”
9.14: ninb Bua i taub zyrug faauj mivb Tauj uaq nxm zivb. ninb Bua yetq pia'g zivb uaq zang, pwatg saa-mu-en Javb Jav yem zivb Zwrtq, huvj Jyenq ninb Bua taaib, xij faauj mivb uaq Jiaj Eei ziab txvb.
9.23: saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj zrub myenb, “tovb yia kxvq, ‘kanb Za'levg lyrub Jyenq’ uaq teij xq kunq txb taaib a'q.”
9.6: mq paag uaq taub pru tau sau-lo, “yem naaiq nxm muvq maaib taub Tinb huvb Eei myenb. myenb za'kevb Taaib haig ninb. ta'faanb ninb kxvq Eei Euvb Euvg zuvq Zwrtq taaib txij Revg. Bua mivb ninb uaq x'g? Riaj ninb haib Buaj Bua yavb haiq tiub Jauq mivb.”
9.2: ninb maaib taub txn, Buaj heug sau-lo, zyavb tu'q lovj, zyavb tu'q Rweig. yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj maiq maaib yetg taub mJavg txn zyavb tu'q Dovg ninb Rweig. yetg zuvq pc'g fivj Bcvg ninb Eei Ba'taub Navq.
9.20: meib Eei lxb, tovb tivj laaib tu'q pua Nxi uaq teij, meib maiq zu'g kwaaj Hruq a'q. zuvq lxd pwatg taaib a'q. i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb maaib Hruq xij lovg Eei se haiq taub? se tovb meib Zauj meib Eei tia Eei trub zov maiq zeid?”
9.24: zrub myenb zyrug txb zaub zwib an Jyenq sau-lo Eei Ra'Myen. saa-mu-en kxvq, “naaiq se lyrub taaib pun meib, yaag an Jyenq meib Eei Ra'Myen. kunq Eang maa'b! weig zu'g yia Zivq Kc'q myenb taaib uaq zang naaiq teij xq lyrub Jyenq Tauj tivg taaib Eei zyavb hog pun meib.” uaq Nxi sau-lo zyrug Zauj saa-mu-en Eang a'q.
9.7: sau-lo kxvq Buaj ninb Eei pru, “sij kxvq mivb lxd ninb, Bua maaib haiq Euvg txb mivb pun uaq laanb myenb? weig zu'g yem Bua Eei Bua'g Eei pyenb fwij Revg mig a'q. Bua maiq maaib haiq Euvg zruj zivb Eeig pun Tinb huvb Eei myenb. Bua maaib teij haiq Euvg fai?”
9.19: saa-mu-en tau sau-lo, “yia se tovb hiuq tu'q zinb hod Eei myenb. meib kunq mivb Daavg yia a'q. faauj mivb yem Lav zavg zyenb Eei txvj, weig zu'g ib Nxi meib xij zu'g Zauj yia Eang Naavj. Fav Dxm yia pun meib Rwrnj yaag zx'q meib yem Hruq Namq Tauj Eei Euvb Euvg sig Buaj meib a'q.
9.17: saa-mu-en pwatg sau-lo uaq zang, zyruq kxvq Buaj ninb, “naaiq se tovb yia kxvq Buaj meib uaq laanb myenb. ninb se tovb xij kunq yia Eei pc'g fivj uaq taub.”
9.27: ninb Bua Fiag Tauj zivb Len uaq zang, saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj sau-lo, “kunq Buaj meib Eei pru mivb Daavg Bua. zuaq ninb Jiaj mivb, meib kanb tivb tavb naaiq zuaq yia zx'q Tinb huvb Eei waag kxvq Buaj meib.”
9.11: ninb Bua faauj Bovb aiq xij pia'g zivb uaq zang, ninb Bua pwavb teij sia'q Zwrtq taaib zaavb uam, zyrug naaig ninb Bua, “hiuq tu'q zinb hod uaq laanb myenb yem naaiq fai?”
9.5: ninb Bua mivb Tauj supg teig uaq zang, sau-lo kxvq Buaj kan ninb Eei pru, “Bua xij zu'g Rwrnj pyauq a'q. Riaj yia Eei tia maiq Raub lxb a'q, taauj Rwrnj ninb Raub Bua.”
9.9: (lob Nxi yem i-saa-laa-en teib puv sij kxvq haiq taub myenb xij mivb naaig Tinb huvb nx, uaq taub myenb kxvq, “taaib maa'b! Bua mivb lxd hiuq tu'q zinb hod Eei sig uaq laanb myenb.” tovb ib Jaaj Nxi Bua heug trug waag myenb, lob Nxi ninb Bua heug hiuq tu'q zinb hod Eei myenb.)
9.16: “Fav Nxi leib maiq ko naaiq nxm zyavb hog, yia xij pun taub Ben-yaa-min teig Eei myenb taaib meib naaiq. meib xij zu'g lovg yrub xn ninb zruj yia Eei pc'g fivj, i-saa-laa-en myenb, Eei pyeiq zeiq. ninb xij Fruj yia Eei pc'g fivj pyauj Dutq fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei puab Diaq. yia pwatg yia Eei pc'g fivj zu'g syrug Kruq weig zu'g ninb Bua heug Jyenq Toq Eei waag Tauj yia Eei mnxmb a'q.”
9.4: ninb Bua i taub zyrug yavb e-faa-im Eei Bovb aiq txvj yaag Jiaj saa-li-saa teig mq paag lxd maiq pwatg. ninb Bua cvj Jiaj saa-aa-lim teig mq paag lxb maiq yem naaig. ninb Bua cvj pia'g Ben-yaa-min Eei teig yaag lxd maiq pwatg uaq teij lxb.
9.10: sau-lo zyrug kxvq Buaj ninb Eei pru, “lovj a'q. taaib maa'b! Bua mivb a'q.” ninb Bua i taub zyrug mivb Tinb huvb Eei myenb yem uaq nxm zivb.
9.22: saa-mu-en zyrug txb sau-lo Zauj sau-lo Eei pru pia'g yetg Qovj pyauq Lo Eei yaag pun ninb Bua zweid Jyenq Kc'q myenb yem uaq nxm txvj Eei tiab kxn. maaib Kc'q myenb leib maiq ko faab zyepg taub.
9.12: uaq teij sia'q tau, “ninb yem Eei. ninb Javb Jav pia'g mivb. sij kxvq meib Bua mivb syepq teij zuvq zung zaaig ninb. ninb Zo'q ho'g pia'g zivb weig zu'g ib Nxi pc'g fivj yem uaq Jiaj Eei ziab txvb fovg hxg ziag.
9.15: sau-lo maiq kcvb Tauj, zinb Daavg uaq Nxi, zyruq zuvq pun saa-mu-en hiuq mig a'q. zyruq kxvq,
9.13: meib Bua i taub yetq pia'g zivb mivb, meib Bua zyrug tu'q pwavb ninb Daavg ninb faauj Tauj yem Lav zavg zyenb Eei txvj Eang Naavj, weig zu'g ninb maiq kcvb Tauj, pc'g fivj zuvq maiq Eang. ninb xij zu'g mivb weig ziag Eei ka'naaiq Toq fu'q Daavg. Ga'haaq Zivq taaib Eei Kc'q myenb Zivj taaib Eang. ib zang kunq faauj mivb a'q. meib Bua zyrug syepg syepq Eei tu'q pwavb ninb.”
9.1: maaib taub Ben-yaa-min fivj Eei myenb, Buaj heug Kitq. Kitq zruj aa-Bi-en Eei txn, sej-lo Eei fun, Be-Ko-latq Eei fa'q. Be-Ko-latq zruj Ben-yaa-min fivj, aa-fi-yaa Eei txn. Kitq se putg zxib myenb.
9.26: ninb Bua i taub Eia Ryruq Eei. luvb Byrub Byrud Fav, saa-mu-en yem pyaub vxb heug sau-lo, “Jiad sin taaib. yia xij fuvj meib Bua Zwrtq Jauq.” sau-lo zyrug Jiad sin. ninb Zauj saa-mu-en Zwrtq Jauq a'q.
9.25: ninb Bua yem uaq Jiaj Eei ziab txvb Fiag taaib pia'g zivb uaq zang, saa-mu-en Zauj sau-lo yem pyaub vxb kub vwaaig kxvq waag.

16.18: maaib taub hrub scv kxvq, “yia pwatg Betg-le-hem myenb, Jyetg-si, maaib taub txn Patq taanb paab lyrug haig. ninb taamq Lo, Bx'q Jaaj henq. ninb kxvq waag Byaavg Eei, Myenb favj yaag zyavb tu'q Rweig. zyruq yaag Zauj ninb yem.”
16.8: Jyetg-si zyrug heug aa-Bi-naa-Dapg yavb Jauq Jiaj saa-mu-en Eei Ra'Myen. saa-mu-en kxvq, “zyruq yaag maiq kinq naaiq taub.”
16.3: Buaj Jyetg-si Zauj Jyenq taaib fovg hxg ziag, yia zyrug Buaj meib, meib hxpg zu'q Navq haiq nx zruj. yia Buaj meib hiuq tu'q haiq taub Eei Buaj, meib xij zu'g lovg yrub xn uaq taub.”
16.21: Daa-witq mivb Tauj sau-lo uaq zyrug zruj huvb tiaj Eei kov. sau-lo Namq haig Daa-witq. Daa-witq yaag tu'q zruj Tevj sau-lo txb ua'g king Eei myenb.
16.14: zyruq Eei sivj livb leib Gxi sau-lo mig a'q. cvj maaib x'q Eei myenq yem zyruq taaib mxb ninb.
16.23: yem Tinb huvb taaib Eei x'q myenq haiq zang taaib mxb sau-lo, Daa-witq zyrug zx'q taanb paab taaib Patq pun sau-lo mwavj. sau-lo zyrug haid Kub yem, lovj a'q. x'q Eei myenq yaag leib Gxi ninb mig a'q.
16.6: Ga'haaq ninb Bua taaib Eei zyavb hog, saa-mu-en mavg pwatg e-li-apg zyrug yem Hruq Namq, “tovb zyruq xn uaq taub Dovg haaij zuvq sruq Jyenq naaiq, zyruq Eei Ra'Myen a'q.”
16.2: saa-mu-en kxvq, “yia Navq haiq nx haib mivb? sij kxvq sau-lo haid nx, ninb zuvq xij taij yia.”   zyruq kxvq, “txb taub yavb vovb Eeid Zauj Jyenq meib mivb yaag kxvq, ‘yia taaib xij fovg hxg ziag pun zyruq.’
16.20: Jyetg-si zyrug Paaiq ninb Eei txn, Daa-witq, mivb yaag zx'q Fuaq Zauj yetg Dopg Bua'g a'vung tiuq Zauj taub yuvb txn pun lxb Tx Jyenq mivb fuvj pun sau-lo.
16.7: mq paag zyruq kxvq Buaj saa-mu-en, “maiq tuvq mavg ninb Eei peib zavg fai ninb Eei sinb Pei zyavb tu'q Lav. yia maiq lovg ninb, weig zu'g zyruq mavg maiq Navq paamb myenb mavg. paamb myenb mavg ka'Eiag peib zavg, mq paag zyruq mavg ka'Euad Hruq.”
16.19: Navq naaig sau-lo zyrug fuvj trug fyenj myenb mivb Buaj Jyetg-si, “Toq pun meib Eei txn, Daa-witq, tovb Zauj pa'ki yuvb yem uaq taub txn, taaib yia naaiq.”
16.17: sau-lo zyrug Buaj ninb Eei pru, “meib Bua kunq mivb weig yia lxd taub haib Patq taanb paab yaaug Eei myenb yaag txb ninb taaib yia naaiq.”
16.11: saa-mu-en naaig Jyetg-si, “meib Eei txn yetg zuvq maaib Bua'g naaiq taub Navq fai?” Jyetg-si tau, “cvj maaib taub txnb laai mq paag ninb mivb puvj pa'ki yuvb mig a'q.” saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj Jyetg-si, “xij zu'g Paaiq myenb mivb heug ninb Rwrnj taaib. ninb maiq kcvb Tauj, yia Bua zuvq maiq zweid.”
16.5: saa-mu-en tau, “yia taaib weig pcvb xn. yia taaib fovg hxg ziag pun zyruq. meib Bua xij zu'g saaj kanb Zivb Revg taaib Zauj yia mivb fovg hxg ziag.” saa-mu-en zyrug saaj Jyetg-si Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua Zivb Revg taaib yaag heug ninb Bua mivb Zauj Jyenq fovg hxg ziag.
16.9: Jyetg-si zyrug heug sam-maa Jiaj mivb, mq paag saa-mu-en kxvq, “zyruq yaag maiq kinq naaiq taub.”
16.16: Toq meib, yia Bua Eei zyruq, Paaiq yem meib Eei Ra'Myen Eei pru mivb lxd taub tovb haib Patq taanb paab lyrug Eei myenb taaib. yem Tinb huvb taaib Eei x'q myenq haiq zang taaib yem huvb tiaj Eei sin nx, heug ninb Patq taanb paab, huvb tiaj zyrug lovj mig a'q.”
16.4: saa-mu-en zyrug ei Jyenq zyruq Eei waag zruj. ninb Tauj Betg-le-hem uaq zang, uaq nxm muvq Eei myenb koj zyrug sin zinj Eanb Eanb Eei Zwrtq taaib zipq ninb yaag naaig kaaj ninb, “meib taaib weig pcvb xn Eei Jauq fai?”
16.10: Jyetg-si heug ninb Eei siag taub txn yavb Jauq Jiaj saa-mu-en Eei Ra'Myen. saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj Jyetg-si, “zyruq maiq kinq naaiq teij myenb.”
16.22: sau-lo fuvj fyenj mivb Buaj Jyetg-si, “Toq pun Daa-witq yem naaiq zruj yia Eei kov, weig zu'g ninb hxpg yia Eei Hruq haig.”
16.12: Jyetg-si zyrug Paaiq myenb mivb heug uaq taub txn Rwrnj taaib. naaiq taub txn se Myenb setq Fav, si'q Eei. Myenb favj zyavb tu'q Rweig. sinb Pei yaag zyavb tu'q lovj.  zyruq kxvq, “tovb naaiq taub a'q. kunq lovg yrub xn ninb maa'b!”
16.15: sau-lo Eei pru Bua zyrug kxvq Buaj sau-lo, “ib zang maaib x'q Eei myenq yem Tinb huvb taaib mxb Jyenq huvb tiaj yem.
16.13: saa-mu-en zyrug zx'q tapq Jyenq Jxv Eei yrub yem uaq taub txn Eei zwavj kxj Bu'Dovj xn ninb. yem uaq Nxi taaib zyruq Eei sivj livb Zamb Zamq Eei yem Jyenq Daa-witq. saa-mu-en zyrug Jiad sin Rwrnj laa-maa mig a'q.
16.1: zyruq kxvq Buaj saa-mu-en, “meib xij weig sau-lo Raub Dovg haaij laub? yia Tutq kwavg ninb, maiq pun ninb zruj huvb kunq i-saa-laa-en myenb. meib xij zu'g zx'q yrub tinb pwavq meib Eei scvb Kuq Jxv zyrug mivb a'q. yia xij Paaiq meib mivb lxd Betg-le-hem myenb, Jyetg-si, weig zu'g yem ninb Eei yetg zuvq txn Eei Bu'Dovj yia weig kanb kinq taub zruj huvb.”

4.18: uaq taub myenb yetq kxvq Tauj Tinb huvb Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav, e-li zyrug yem zivb kcvb ka'Len, ninb zweid Eei txvj uaq, ta'Ryaauj Kiv Ga'haaq mcvj. ninb Eei Jaav nauq, zyrug taig mig a'q, weig zu'g ninb koj haig, sinb sei yaag Niaq. e-li zruj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei tomb Jyen feij zyepg Havj.
4.8: Bua xij zu'g Kruq a'q. haiq taub haib Tevj Bua pyauj Dutq naaiq teij henq haig Eei zyenb? tovb naaiq teij zyenb zinb Daavg yem teib puvb Waav lovg Euvb Euvg ze'g naang taij taig i-yipq myenb.
4.3: i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei pcv Rwrnj Tauj Zyavq uaq zang, i-saa-laa-en Eei myenb koj kxvq, “zyruq ib Nxi weig haiq tiug pun Bua swei fi-li-saa-tia myenb? xij zu'g mivb si-lo txb zyruq Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav taaib weig pun zyruq taaib yem Bua Bu'Dovj, Tevj Bua pyauj Dutq winb wavq Eei puab Diaq.”
4.21: ninb Tevj ninb Eei txn Zwrtq Buaj heug i-Kaa-Botg yaag kxvq, “Favb laavg leib Gxi i-saa-laa-en mig a'q.” weig zu'g Tinb huvb Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav zu'g Zaavq mivb, ninb Eei ovb puag Zauj ninb Eei Goj yaag taig mig a'q.
4.14: e-li haid myenb heug Eei Qiaj Bwi zyrug naaig, “zruj haiq Euvg Byrub Byrub Eei heug Dovg naaig Bwi?” txb fyenj uaq taub myenb zyrug kaanq Jyenq taaib Buaj fyenj e-li.
4.6: fi-li-saa-tia myenb mwavj haid heug Eei Qiaj Bwi, ninb Bua kxvq, “yem hipq-lu myenb Eei Zyavq fuvg maaib heug Eei Qiaj Dovg naaig Bwi? zruj haiq Euvg mq pei?” Ga'haaq ninb Bua hiuq tu'q i-saa-laa-en myenb txb zyruq Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav taaib Tauj Zyavq mig a'q.
4.2: fi-li-saa-tia myenb pun ninb Bua Eei pcv txv Jyenq i-saa-laa-en myenb Baib Jyenq. Bx'q Jaaj kunq zruj kunq Lo Eei zyavb hog, i-saa-laa-en myenb swei fi-li-saa-tia myenb. fi-li-saa-tia myenb yem uaq Bx'q Jaaj Zyavq taij taig leib maiq ko pyei Zin taub i-saa-laa-en myenb.
4.20: tovb ninb aaq lamb tavj Qiaj uaq zang, Tevj kruj ninb uaq teij msia'q txn kxvq Buaj ninb, “maiq tuvq kamb Riaj og, weig zu'g meib yuvd tu'q taub txn.” mq paag ninb maiq tau, yaag Navq mwavj maiq haid nx.
4.7: fi-li-saa-tia myenb kamb Riaj haig. ninb Bua kxvq, “maaib taub zyenb taaib Tauj Zyavq mig a'q.” ninb Bua cvj kxvq, “Bua xij zu'g Kruq a'q, weig zu'g Bua maiq pwavb Jiaj naaiq Euvg sig.
4.19: uaq zang e-li Eei Bwavd, fi-ne-hatg Eei auq, maaib Jyenq sin aaq lamb Tauj Dutq sin Eei zyavb hog. ninb haid fyenj kxvq Tinb huvb Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav zu'g Zaavq mivb, ninb Eei ovb puag Zauj ninb Eei Goj yaag taig mig a'q. ninb zyrug lyemb zeib mun kub vwaad, yuvd tu'q taub txn. ninb za'kevb mun tu'q Kruq haig.
4.17: txb fyenj Eei myenb tau, “i-saa-laa-en myenb yem fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei uaq Daavg mcvj pyauj. yem pc'g fivj Eei Bu'Dovj myenb zu'g taij taig Zamq haig. meib Eei i taub txn, hopq-ni Zauj fi-ne-hatg, yaag zu'g taig mig a'q. Tinb huvb Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav yaag zu'g Zaavq mivb mig a'q.”
4.11: Tinb huvb Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav yaag zu'g Zaavq mivb. e-li Eei i taub txn, hopq-ni Zauj fi-ne-hatg, yaag zu'g taij taig mig a'q.
4.5: zyruq Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav pia'g Zyavq ka'Euad uaq zang, i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb Qa'q heug Qiaj Bwi Eei, zuvq Dang zu'g Dau tovd.
4.9: o fi-li-saa-tia myenb aa'b! meib Bua xij zu'g zuvj taamq yaag zruj Junb zeiq myenb. maiq zei c'q, meib Bua zu'g zruj hipq-lu myenb Eei nrub Navq zinb Daavg ninb Bua zruj meib Bua Eei nrub nx. xij zu'g zruj Junb zeiq myenb Zwrtq mivb Bx'q Jaaj.”
4.16: uaq taub myenb kxvq Buaj e-li, “se tovb yia yem Bx'q Jaaj Zyavq taaib. ib Nxi yia yem Bx'q Jaaj Eei zyavb hog pyauj Rwrnj.” e-li naaig, “aa txn aag, Navq haiq nx?”
4.4: ninb Bua zyrug Paaiq myenb mivb si-lo uaq, txb lcvd vcvg waag faav taaib, se maaib nrnb Jiaj Eei zyruq yem uaq teij i taub Ke-lu-Bim Bu'Dovj Eei weig Eei faav. e-li Eei i taub txn, hopq-ni Zauj fi-ne-hatg, Zauj Jyenq Tinb huvb Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav taaib.
4.10: fi-li-saa-tia myenb zyrug Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb Bx'q Jaaj. i-saa-laa-en myenb swei ninb Bua, kx'g myenb pyauj Rwrnj kx'g myenb kanb Eei Dopg liub mivb. uaq Rung za'kevb maaib pcv Zamq Eei zu'g taij taig, weig zu'g i-saa-laa-en Eei pua waang taub yavb Dau pcv zu'g taij taig mig a'q.
4.22: ninb cvj kxvq, “Favb laavg leib Gxi i-saa-laa-en, weig zu'g Tinb huvb Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav zu'g Zaavq mivb mig a'q.”
4.12: tovb uaq Nxi maaib taub Ben-yaa-min fivj Eei myenb yem Bx'q Jaaj Zyavq Tiuj mivb Tauj si-lo. ninb Eei lwib hruj petq huq, mGxvq yaag maaib niab Buv Yaamj Jyenq.
4.15: uaq zang e-li Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Juaq zyepg petq Havj. ninb Eei mziv tivg mig a'q, mavg maiq pwatg haiq Euvg.
4.13: naaiq taub myenb taaib Tauj uaq zang, e-li yem uaq Jaub Len zweid Jyenq ninb kanb Eei txvj zuaq mavg. ninb weig Tinb huvb Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav Hruq Waav. uaq taub myenb pia'g zivb taaib Buaj fyenj, yem zivb Eei yetg zuvq myenb naug Jiad taaib.
4.1: saa-mu-en Eei waag zyrug mivb kxmj i-saa-laa-en teib puv. i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq mivb Zauj fi-li-saa-tia myenb Bx'q Jaaj. ninb Bua lyepg Zyavq yem e-Ben-e-se. fi-li-saa-tia myenb lyepg Zyavq yem aa-fekq.

10.18: saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, “zyruq, i-saa-laa-en Eei Tinb huvb, Navq naaiq nx kxvq, ‘yia yem i-yipq teib puv txb i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq taaib, yaag Fruj meib Bua pyauj Dutq i-yipq myenb Eei puab Diaq, cvj Fruj meib Bua pyauj Dutq tovb hxig meib Bua uaq teij nxmb nxm kua'q Eei myenb Eei puab Diaq.’
10.8: “meib xij zu'g mivb kin-kaan Daavg yia. Ga'haaq yia yaag mivb uaq pwavb meib, weig fovg hxg puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq Zauj ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq. meib xij zu'g yem naaig zuaq siag Nxi, yia zyrug mivb meib uaq yaag pun meib hiuq tu'q meib xij zu'g Navq haiq nx zruj.”
10.3: “meib cvj Jiaj mivb teij Tauj Taa-Bo, tomb Ba'ov zwei Dyavj uaq. yem naaig meib zyrug pwavb zu'g pua laanb myenb xij mivb Betg-en zavg Tinb huvb. maaib laanb myenb Lxpq pua taub yuvb txn, maaib laanb txb pua nxm Fuaq, cvj maaib laanb txb yetg Dopg Bua'g a'vung tiuq.
10.21: ninb zyrug txb Ben-yaa-min fivj taaib, ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng, cvj tivg mcvg mavg, Dxtq zu'g maa-ti Eei trub zov. setq mweid Dxtq zu'g Kitq Eei txn, sau-lo, mq paag ninb Bua lxd sau-lo maiq pwatg.
10.14: sau-lo Eei pc'q naaig sau-lo Zauj ninb Eei pru, “meib Bua mivb haaij taaib?” sau-lo tau, “yia Bua mivb lxd lxb. lxd kau maiq pwatg, yia Bua zyrug mivb lxd saa-mu-en.”
10.23: zwavj myenb zyrug Tiuj mivb Ken ninb taaib. ninb sruq Jyenq zwavj pc'g fivj Bu'Dovj, yetg zuvq pc'g fivj Bcvg ninb Eei Ba'taub Navq.
10.6: zyruq Eei sivj livb xij Zamb Zamq Eei yem meib. meib yaag xij Zauj Jyenq uaq teij trug waag myenb trug waag. meib zyrug Tiuq penj syavb myenb.
10.2: meib ib Nxi Zauj yia leib Gxi txig uaq zang, yem Ben-yaa-min teig ka'Euad Eei senj-saa, nitq fatq laa-sen Eei zruq, meib xij pwavb i laanb myenb. ninb Bua xij kxvq Buaj meib, ‘tovb meib mivb lxd uaq teij lxb zuvq lxd pwatg taaib a'q. ib zang meib Eei tia maiq Raub lxb. taauj Rwrnj ninb Raub meib. ninb kxvq, “yia Eei txn ni? yia xij zu'g Navq haiq nx zruj?”+’
10.20: saa-mu-en txb i-saa-laa-en Eei fivb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb taaib, zyrug tivg mcvg mavg, Dxtq zu'g Ben-yaa-min fivj.
10.24: saa-mu-en zyrug kxvq Buaj yetg zuvq pc'g fivj, “meib Bua pwatg tovb zyruq kinq taaib Eei myenb a'q fai? yetg zuvq pc'g fivj maiq maaib haiq taub Navq ninb.” zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug heug Qiaj Bwi Eei kxvq, “Toq pun huvb tiaj zyavb tu'q maang fwij a'q.”
10.7: meib pwatg naaiq teij Javb hog Zwrtq taaib uaq zang, ziuj meib pwatg hxpg zu'g zruj Eei kunq zruj a'q, weig zu'g Tinb huvb Zauj meib yem.
10.19: mq paag ib Nxi meib Bua kwavg meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, tovb Fruj meib Bua pyauj Dutq yetg zuvq Kruq naang Zauj Kwrnj Hruq Eei sig uaq taub. meib Bua kxvq, ‘yia Bua maiq Kavq. Toq lyepg taub huvb tiaj taaib kunq yia Bua.’ Navq naaig, ib zang meib Bua xij zu'g ziuj meib Bua Eei fivj yaag ziuj meib Bua Eei puvb pwrng taaib yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen.”
10.17: saa-mu-en zyrug heug zwavj pc'g fivj kapq zunq taaib yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen, mitq-paa uaq.
10.27: mq paag maaib teij Zeuj lung Eei myenb kxvq, “naaiq taub myenb Navq haiq nx haib Fruj tu'q Bua?” ninb Bua zyrug mavg Piaj sau-lo, maiq fuvj zivb Eeig pun ninb. mq paag sau-lo maiq Ko lo.
10.11: tovb zinb Daavg hiuq tu'q sau-lo uaq teij myenb pwatg ninb Zauj Jyenq trug waag myenb trug waag, laanb Zauj laanb kxvq, “Kitq Eei txn fuvg Navq naaiq nx x'b? sau-lo yaag penj taub trug waag myenb fai?”
10.5: “meib Bua cvj Jiaj mivb Tauj Tinb huvb Eei Bov, ki-Be-aa. yem uaq maaib nxm fi-li-saa-tia myenb kruj teib puv pcv Eei zaamg. meib mivb Tauj uaq nxm zivb Eei zyavb hog, meib zyrug pwavb zu'g yetg kwanb trug waag myenb yem uaq Jiaj Eei ziab txvb Fiag taaib. maaib teij Patq tomb taanb paab, fiub taanb paab, Bx'q Rod, pyomq Laub Dovb nuj yend Jauq taaib Daavg. ninb Bua yaag trug Jyenq Tinb huvb Eei waag taaib.
10.9: sau-lo kwinb sin leib Gxi saa-mu-en uaq zang, Tinb huvb kxiq yeng sau-lo Eei Hruq. uaq Nxi naaiq teij yetg zuvq Javb hog Zwrtq taaib txij Revg.
10.16: sau-lo tau ninb Eei pc'q, “saa-mu-en mevb mevb Eei kxvq Buaj yia Bua, ‘uaq teij lxb lxd pwatg taaib a'q.’+” mq paag tovb saa-mu-en kxvq Tauj kua'q zavg Eei Jaub lrug, ninb maiq kxvq yetg teij pun ninb Eei pc'q mwavj.
10.4: ninb Bua zyrug kxvq wig pwavb waag cvj zx'q i nxm Fuaq Zunq pun meib. meib yaag xij zu'g yem ninb Bua Eei puad zipq taaib.
10.10: sau-lo Zauj ninb Eei pru mivb Tauj ki-Be-aa uaq zang, maaib kwanb trug waag myenb pwavb zu'g ninb. Tinb huvb Eei sivj livb zyrug Zamb Zamq Eei Fiag taaib yem Jyenq ninb. ninb zyrug yem uaq teij trug waag myenb Bu'Dovj trug waag.
10.22: ninb Bua zyrug naaig zyruq, “uaq laanb myenb taaib naaiq fai?”   zyruq kxvq, “ninb pivj Jyenq ka'naaib Dwi ka'Euad.”
10.12: yem uaq maaib taub myenb tau, “ninb Bua Eei tia se haiq taub?” weig naaig, Ga'haaq naaiq Jruj waag, “sau-lo yaag penj taub trug waag myenb fai?” penj waab Pwij mig a'q.
10.15: sau-lo Eei pc'q kxvq, “saa-mu-en kxvq haiq Euvg Buaj meib? kxvq Buaj yia kaaj.”
10.13: sau-lo trug liud waag uaq zang, ninb faauj Tauj uaq Jiaj Eei ziab txvb.
10.1: saa-mu-en zyrug zx'q pcvb lovg xn myenb Eei yrub taaib toj Fiag sau-lo Eei mGxvq cvj zom ninb Eei Myen yaag kxvq, “naaiq se zyruq ib Nxi lovg yrub xn meib zruj pyeiq zeiq kunq ninb Ripg Eei pwrng maiq zeid fai?”
10.26: sau-lo yaag Rwrnj ki-Be-aa zivb, ninb kanb Eei pyauq uaq. maaib teij Bx'q Jaaj henq Eei pcv, Tinb huvb pun ninb Bua maaib Hruq xij kan Jyenq sau-lo mivb.
10.25: saa-mu-en zyrug kxvq mevb pun pc'g fivj hiuq tu'q huvb tiaj maaib leid zruj haiq Euvg, huvb tiaj Eei kov yaag xij zu'g Navq haiq nx. ninb zyrug fiaq Fiag sru an Jyenq zyruq Eei Ra'Myen. Ga'haaq saa-mu-en heug pc'g fivj, kx'g myenb Rwrnj kx'g myenb Eei pyauq.

22.18: huvb tiaj zyrug kxvq Buaj Do-ekg, “meib mivb taij uaq teij sai myenb maa'b!” e-Dom myenb, Do-ekg, zyrug mivb taij uaq teij sai myenb. uaq Nxi ninb lovg Ru'g Daauq taij zu'q la'maab Dia e-fotq Eei myenb petq zyepg Mmd taub.
22.8: se weig naaiq meib Bua Zivj taaib peig Diaq Zaavb laavb xij hxig yia? yia Eei txn Zauj Jyetg-si Eei txn taaq lob kcv Eei zyavb hog maiq maaib haiq taub Buaj yia, Tevj yia Raub. yaag maiq maaib haiq taub pun yia hiuq tu'q yia Eei txn Zo'q yia Eei pru hxig yia, zuaq Jyenq zx'q yia Navq ib Nxi nx.”
22.3: Daa-witq zyrug Zwrtq uaq nxm txvj mivb mo-apg kua'q, mitq-paa uaq nxm txvj. ninb kxvq Buaj mo-apg Eei huvb tiaj, “Toq pun yia Eei tia maa taaib Zauj meib yem naaiq, zuaq Tauj yia hiuq tu'q Tinb huvb xij weig yia zruj haiq Euvg.”
22.21: aa-Bi-yaa-Taa yaag kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, sau-lo taij zyruq Eei sai myenb mig a'q.
22.14: aa-hi-me-lekq tau huvb tiaj, “yem huvb tiaj Eei zwavj pru Bu'Dovj uaq teij zruj Jyen Eei myenb maaib haiq taub haib Dovg huvb tiaj Eei sia'g laavb, Daa-witq, Hruq zivj? ninb zruj kruj huvb tiaj uaq teij pcv Eei pyeiq. yem meib Eei pyauq zov ka'Euad Eei yetg zuvq myenb yaag Taaib ninb.
22.23: meib kunq Zauj yia yem naaiq a'q. maiq tuvq kamb Riaj weig zu'g xij zx'q meib Eei mcvg uaq taub yaag xij zx'q yia. meib Zauj yia yem naaiq nx, meib zyrug pyauj Dutq mcvg a'q.”
22.6: sau-lo haid kxvq maaib myenb tu'q pwatg Daa-witq Zauj kan ninb Eei myenb. uaq zang sau-lo yem ki-Be-aa teig, zweid Jyenq zxv kub vwaaig Eei linb lyrud Dyavj ka'Diaq nanq Jyenq Zav. ninb Eei pru sruq Jyenq weib kxmj ninb.
22.2: ta'faanb zu'g Kruq Eei myenb Zauj Qyemj zc'q Eei myenb Zauj maiq pwavq Hruq Eei myenb taaib lxd ninb. Daa-witq zruj uaq teij zwavj myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq. taaib kan ninb Eei myenb maaib leib maiq ko feij pc'q taub.
22.20: mq paag maaib taub aa-hi-Tupq Eei fun, aa-hi-me-lekq Eei txn, Buaj heug aa-Bi-yaa-Taa, pyauj Dutq zyrug mivb Tauj Daa-witq uaq.
22.7: sau-lo zyrug kxvq Buaj sruq weib kxmj ninb uaq teij pru, “Ben-yaa-min myenb aa'b! mwavj maa'b! Jyetg-si Eei txn xij zx'q livb teig Zauj a'vung Wivj Jiu pun meib Bua kx'g myenb fai? ninb xij lyepg meib Bua kx'g myenb zruj pcvb pyeiq kunq yetg Zin taub pcv fai yetg pc'q taub pcv fai?
22.19: ninb lovg Ru'g Daauq cvj taij sai myenb Eei muvq, nopq, Eei mJavg msia'q, fu'Jweiq Zauj kub vwaad, lyemb vovb, lxb Zauj pa'ki yuvb.
22.17: huvb tiaj zyrug Paaiq sruq Jyenq ninb Eei ka'Len uaq teij sinb Len myenb, “Win mivb taij Revg zyruq Eei naaiq teij sai myenb maa'b! weig zu'g ninb Bua Tevj Daa-witq uaq puv. ninb Bua hiuq tu'q Daa-witq pyauj, yaag maiq mivb Buaj yia.” mq paag huvb tiaj Eei sinb Len myenb maiq Kavq Fiag puad taij zyruq Eei sai myenb.
22.11: sau-lo zyrug Paaiq myenb mivb heug aa-hi-Tupq Eei txn, aa-hi-me-lekq sai myenb Zauj aa-hi-me-lekq Eei tia Eei trub zov myenb, tovb yem nopq zruj sai myenb uaq teij. ninb Bua yetg zuvq zyrug taaib huvb tiaj uaq.
22.5: trug waag myenb, kaatg, kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “meib maiq tuvq yem naaiq a'q. kaanq mivb yu-Daa teib puv yem.” Daa-witq zyrug leib Gxi uaq nxm txvj mivb yem he-letq-Ti lomg.
22.9: e-Dom myenb, Do-ekg sruq nitq Jyenq sau-lo Eei pru. ninb kxvq, “yia pwatg Jyetg-si Eei txn yem nopq uaq, lxd aa-hi-Tupq Eei txn, aa-hi-me-lekq.
22.16: huvb tiaj kxvq, “aa-hi-me-lekq aa'b! meib Dovg haaij zuvq xij zu'g taig a'q, lyemb meib Zauj meib Eei tia Eei trub zov myenb.”
22.4: Daa-witq zyrug txb ninb Eei tia maa taaib Zauj mo-apg Eei huvb yem. ta'faanb Daa-witq Zxg pivj Jyenq yem Eei zyavb hog, ninb Eei tia maa Zauj mo-apg Eei huvb yem.
22.10: aa-hi-me-lekq Tevj Daa-witq naaig zyruq yaag pun Eang hopq Zauj fi-li-saa-tia myenb, ko-li-atg, Eei Ru'g Daauq ninb.”
22.22: Daa-witq kxvq Buaj aa-Bi-yaa-Taa, “uaq Nxi yia pwatg e-Dom myenb, Do-ekg, yem uaq, yia hiuq tu'q ninb Dovg haaij zuvq xij Buaj sau-lo. se laaij yia meib Eei tia Eei trub zov myenb Zivj zu'g taij taig Revg.
22.12: sau-lo zyrug kxvq, “aa-hi-Tupq Eei txn aa'b! mwavj maa'b!” aa-hi-me-lekq tau sau-lo, “yia Eei zyruq aa'b! yia yem naaiq og.”
22.15: uaq Nxi yia Tevj ninb naaig Tinb huvb taaub Rung fai? zuvq maiq zeid? Toq huvb tiaj maiq tuvq tivg yia, meib Eei pru fai meib Eei pru Eei tia Eei trub zov haiq taub maaib Eei zwid, weig zu'g yia, meib Eei pru, maiq hiuq haiq Euvg Tauj naaiq teij sig.”
22.13: sau-lo kxvq Buaj ninb, “meib weig haiq tiug Zauj Jyetg-si Eei txn kapq zunq txig Zaavb laavb hxig yia? meib pun Fuaq Zauj Ru'g Daauq ninb, yaag Tevj ninb naaig Tinb huvb, ninb zyrug vcvg yia, zuaq Jyenq xij zx'q yia Navq ib Nxi nx.”
22.1: Daa-witq Zwrtq katg zivb pyauj mivb yem aa-Dun-lam Bcvb Kwrtq. ninb Eei kxj Bua Zauj ninb Eei tia Eei pyauq zov myenb mwavj haid, ninb Bua zyrug mivb uaq lxd ninb.

12.18: saa-mu-en zyrug Toq zyruq. uaq Nxi zyruq pun luvb pxvd Ba'ov, twib Byuvg. zwavj pc'g fivj za'kevb kamb Riaj haig zyruq Zauj saa-mu-en.
12.8: “yaa-Kopq pia'g i-yipq teib puv uaq zang, meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij heug Jyenq Toq zyruq.  zyruq zyrug Paaiq mo-se Zauj aa-lon. ninb Bua txb meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij yem i-yipq teib puv Zwrtq taaib yem naaiq nxm teib puv.
12.3: yia yem naaiq. Toq meib Bua yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Zauj ninb lovg yrub xn taaib zruj huvb uaq taub Eei Ra'Myen Tevj yia zruj zxvb zevj. yia zx'q Jiaj haiq taub Eei vovb fai? yia Zaavq Jiaj haiq taub Eei lxb fai? yia Kwei Jiaj haiq taub fai? yia zeij Jiaj haiq taub fai? yia yem haiq taub Eei puad zipq Jiaj Eaanb Mwavj zyrug zruj pun yia Eei mziv mcvb Eei fai? kunq kxvq a'q. yia zyrug Twij Rwrnj pun meib Bua.”
12.21: maiq tuvq Win mivb kan maiq lamb lovg Eei zyenb. ninb Bua maiq haib Tevj meib Bua tu'q lovj, yaag maiq haib Fruj meib Bua, weig zu'g ninb Bua maiq lamb lovg.
12.14: sij kxvq meib Bua Taaib zyruq yaag fub suj ninb, mwavj ninb Eei waag, maiq vcvg ninb Eei livg, meib Bua Zauj kunq meib Bua Eei huvb tiaj yaag kan lovj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zyrug lovj a'q.
12.23: yia kanb xij zu'g weig meib Bua maiq tivb lyrub Eei tauj kauj. maiq zei c'q, yia paamd zwid txvg zyruq. yia yaag xij Faauj meib Bua hiuq tu'q haiq Euvg lovj Eei, hxpg zu'g zruj Eei Jauq.
12.6: saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj pc'g fivj, “zinb Daavg zyruq lyepg mo-se Zauj aa-lon yaag txb meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij yem i-yipq teib puv Zwrtq taaib.
12.2: ib zang meib Bua maaib huvb txb meib Bua. yia kanb Havb Jeiq koj, Ba'pyei pc'g a'q. yia Eei txn Bua yaag Zauj meib Bua yem naaiq. yem yia lunj Eei zyavb hog Tauj ib Nxi yia txb meib Bua.
12.20: saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj pc'g fivj, “maiq tuvq kamb Riaj. maiq kunq meib Bua zruj naaiq teij yetg zuvq x'q sig mq paag meib Bua maiq tuvq leib Gxi zyruq. xij zu'g lovg Revg meib Bua Eei Hruq fub suj zyruq.
12.24: meib Bua xij zu'g Taaib zyruq, lovg Revg Hruq zyepg zua'q Eei fub suj ninb. xij zu'g Javj Jyenq ninb weig meib Bua zruj Lo haig Eei sig.
12.7: Navq naaig, ib zang meib Bua xij zu'g sruq Jyenq tivg Eei. yia xij txv Jyenq zyruq koj meib Bua, pun meib Bua Javj zyruq weig meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij zruj Eei yetg zuvq Kuq sig.
12.19: zwavj pc'g fivj kxvq Buaj saa-mu-en, “Toq weig yia Bua, meib Eei pru, tauj kauj Toq zyruq, meib Eei Tinb huvb, pun yia Bua maiq zu'g taig, weig zu'g yia Bua Toq lyepg taub huvb tiaj za'kevb penj x'q sig Jaa Jyenq yia Bua Eei yetg zuvq zwid.”
12.17: ib Nxi maiq zeid syru Byaub witq Eei zyavb hog fai? yia xij Toq zyruq pun luvb pxvd Ba'ov, twib Byuvg, pun meib Bua hiuq tu'q yaag samj tu'q Zwrtq ziuj zyruq mavg, meib Bua Toq lyepg huvb, meib Bua zruj x'q sig Dovg haaij Lo.”
12.11: zyruq Paaiq ye-lupq-Baa-an, Baa-laakq, yepq-Taa Zauj saa-mu-en, yaag Fruj meib Bua pyauj Dutq faamb puv feij lrug uaq teij winb wavq Eei puab Diaq. meib Bua zyrug tu'q Taaib pcvb Eei yem.
12.5: saa-mu-en zyrug kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “ib Nxi zyruq Zauj ninb lovg yrub xn taaib uaq taub, txv Jyenq meib Bua zruj zxvb zevj kxvq, ‘meib Bua maiq pwatg yia maaib haiq Euvg txvg Eei txvj.’+” yetg zuvq pc'g fivj kxvq, “zyruq zruj zxvb zevj mig a'q.”
12.9: “mq paag ninb Bua la'Ku'q zyruq, ninb Bua Eei Tinb huvb mig a'q. ninb zyrug zx'q ninb Bua Jiu pun yem haa-so zivb Eei huvb, yaa-Bin, Eei tomb pcvb pyeiq, si-sej-laa Eei puab Diaq, yaag Jiu pun yem fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei puab Diaq, yaag Jiu pun yem mo-apg Eei huvb tiaj Eei puab Diaq. ninb Bua zyrug Zauj meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij Bx'q Jaaj.
12.16: “Navq naaig, ib zang meib Bua sruq tivg mavg Jyenq zyruq xij yem meib Bua Eei Ra'Myen zruj Lo haig Eei sig.
12.4: zwavj myenb kxvq, “meib maiq Kwei Jiaj yia Bua, yaag maiq zeij Jiaj yia Bua, yaag maiq yem haiq taub Eei puad zipq Jiaj haiq Euvg.”
12.10: meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij heug Jyenq Toq zyruq yaag kxvq, ‘yia Bua paamd zwid mig a'q, weig zu'g yia Bua kwavg zyruq mivb fub suj Baa-an zyenb Zauj atg-Taa-lotq zyenb. mq paag ib zang Toq Fruj yia Bua pyauj Dutq yia Bua Eei winb wavq Eei puab Diaq. yia Bua zyrug fub suj zyruq. ’
12.22: zyruq weig ninb kanb Lo haig Eei mevb maiq kwavg ninb Eei myenb, weig zu'g zyruq a'Neiq pun meib Bua penj ninb kanb Eei pc'g fivj.
12.12: “meib Bua pwatg am-mon myenb Eei huvb, naa-haatg, taaib Bx'q meib Bua uaq zang, maiq kunq maaib zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zruj meib Bua Eei huvb tiaj, meib Bua kxvq Buaj yia, ‘maiq zeid! yia Bua xij lovg taub myenb zruj huvb tiaj kunq yia Bua.’
12.15: mq paag sij kxvq meib Bua maiq mwavj zyruq Eei waag yaag vcvg zyruq Eei livg, zyruq Eei puad zyrug Zauj meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei huvb tiaj txib tekg.
12.13: mavg maa'b! ib zang naaiq se meib Bua kinq taaib Eei huvb tiaj, tovb meib Bua Toq taaib uaq taub. zyruq lyepg taub huvb taaib kunq meib Bua.
12.1: saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb, “yia mwavj meib Bua kxvq Eei yetg zuvq waag yaag lyepg taub huvb tiaj kunq meib Bua.
12.25: mq paag sij kxvq meib Bua cvj zruj Jyenq x'q sig yem nx, meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei huvb tiaj zuvq xij zu'g myetg a'q.”

15.18: zyruq Paaiq meib Zwrtq mivb yaag hatg meib, ‘mivb a'q! xij zu'g myetg Revg aa-maa-lekq myenb, se paamd zwid Eei myenb. xij zu'g Bx'q Tauj ninb Bua zutg Revg.’
15.8: ninb lovg Ru'g Daauq taij Revg aa-maa-lekq pc'g fivj, yaag zx'q tu'q aa-maa-lekq myenb Eei huvb, aa-kakg, maiq taij.
15.33: saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj aa-kakg, “meib Eei Ru'g Daauq Navq haiq nx zruj pun msia'q txn kwavg fu'Jweiq, meib Eei maa yem zwavj msia'q txn Bu'Dovj yaag fib Navq Eei xij zu'g kwavg fu'Jweiq.” saa-mu-en zyrug yem kin-kaan txv Jyenq zyruq Va'q aa-kakg penj ziaj Ganj, ziaj Ganj Eei.
15.3: ib zang meib mivb Bx'q aa-maa-lekq myenb, yaag myetg Revg ninb Bua maaib Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq. maiq tuvq lyrub yetg Euvg. xij zu'g taij Revg mJavg, msia'q, fu'Jweiq Zauj hopq Jyenq Exj Eei kub vwaad. lyemb vovb, pa'ki yuvb, lxb Txb Zauj lxb xij zu'g taij Revg.’+”
15.32: saa-mu-en kxvq, “meib Bua xij zu'g txb aa-maa-lekq myenb Eei huvb, aa-kakg, taaib yia naaiq.” aa-kakg zyrug Fav Myen Fav mweig Eei taaib yem saa-mu-en Eei Ra'Myen. aa-kakg yem Hruq Namq, “yia pyauj Dutq zu'g taig Eei Kruq naang mig a'q.”
15.21: mq paag pc'g fivj zx'q Zaavq taaib Eei ka'naaiq, se pa'ki yuvb, vovb Zauj xij zu'g myetg kaub lovj Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq, txb taaib weig yem kin-kaan lovg ziag pun zyruq, meib Eei Tinb huvb.”
15.35: saa-mu-en Tauj ninb kwei seij Eei Nxi, maiq taaib pwavb sau-lo. mq paag saa-mu-en weig sau-lo Hruq mun haig. zyruq yaag Namb Rwrnj weig zu'g ninb lyepg sau-lo zruj huvb kunq i-saa-laa-en myenb.
15.14: saa-mu-en kxvq, “uaq Euvg, pa'ki yuvb heug Eei Qiaj pia'g yia Eei mnxmb. yia yaag haid vovb heug Eei Qiaj. maaib haiq Euvg eij leid?”
15.23: laaij myenb vcvg zyruq se Navq Bruq kwaaj Eei zwid. zruj mauj se x'q Eei zwid Navq paaij miub favj. laaij meib kwavg zyruq Eei waag, zyruq Zivj taaib Tutq meib Eei huvb weig.”
15.6: sau-lo kxvq Buaj Ke-nai myenb, “mivb a'q. meib Bua xij zu'g simq Gxi aa-maa-lekq myenb. Riaj yia pun meib Bua Zauj ninb Bua yetg Fiag zu'g myetg Revg. weig zu'g i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv uaq zang meib Bua Kxb lyenb ninb Bua.” Ke-nai myenb zyrug leib Gxi aa-maa-lekq myenb mig a'q.
15.34: saa-mu-en zyrug mivb laa-maa zivb mig a'q. sau-lo yaag Rwrnj ninb kanb Eei pyauq yem sau-lo Eei pwrnb zivb, ki-Be-aa.
15.2: nrnb Jiaj Eei zyruq Navq naaiq kxvq, ‘yia xij tivg aa-maa-lekq myenb Eei zwid weig zu'g zinb Daavg i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv Eei zyavb hog, aa-maa-lekq myenb tavq Jyenq i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei Jauq.
15.20: sau-lo kxvq Buaj saa-mu-en, “yia za'kevb mwavj zyruq Eei waag yaag ei Jyenq zyruq Paaiq yia mivb zruj Eei zruj. yia zx'q tu'q aa-maa-lekq myenb Eei huvb, aa-kakg, taaib yaag myetg Revg aa-maa-lekq myenb.
15.24: sau-lo kxvq Buaj saa-mu-en, “yia paamd zwid mig a'q, weig zu'g yia vcvg Jyenq zyruq Eei livg Zauj meib Eei waag. yia kamb Riaj pc'g fivj Zivj taaib mwavj ninb Bua.
15.28: saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj sau-lo, “ib Nxi zyruq petq i-saa-laa-en kua'q Zwrtq meib Eei puab Diaq mig a'q, yaag Jiu pun kanb taub kaub lovj meib.
15.7: sau-lo zyrug Bx'q hivb aa-maa-lekq myenb, yem haa-wi-laa mivb Tauj su-waa, yem i-yipq Eei tov puv mcvj uaq.
15.29: i-saa-laa-en Eei Qa'q uaq taub, maiq kxvb pc'g yaag maiq kxiq za'eij, weig zu'g ninb maiq zeid paamb myenb. ninb maiq kxiq za'eij.”
15.19: meib weig haiq tiug maiq mwavj zyruq Eei waag? meib weig haiq tiug kaanq Jyenq Zaavq ka'naaiq, ziuj zyruq mavg zruj waaig sig?”
15.17: saa-mu-en zyrug kxvq, “maiq kunq meib pwatg kanb penj faib fiuq myenb, meib tu'q zruj fivb fivj i-saa- laa-en myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq maiq zeid? zyruq lovg yrub xn meib zruj huvb kunq i-saa-laa-en myenb.
15.31: saa-mu-en zyrug Zauj Jyenq sau-lo Rwrnj. sau-lo yaag zavg zyruq.

15.5: sau-lo zyrug mivb Tauj aa-maa-lekq myenb Eei zivb, yem uaq hxvd pivj Jyenq.
15.9: mq paag sau-lo Zauj pc'g fivj lyrub aa-kakg Eei mcvg, yaag lyrub kaub lovj Jiaj Eei pa'ki yuvb, vovb, vovb txnb Jung Zauj pa'ki yuvb txn cvj Zauj yetg zuvq lovj Eei ka'naaiq, maiq Kavq myetg. Kuvj myetg mavg Piaj Eei, maiq zig zinb Eei ka'naaiq Navq.

15.4: weig naaiq sau-lo tiug Rxib pcv taaib yem Te-laa-im. ninb saauq yavb Dau Eei pcv, maaib Eig zyepg waang taub. yu-Daa fivj maaib yetg waang taub.

15.12: ta'Eeig Dxm saa-mu-en Jiad sin Ryruq Eei xij mivb lxd sau-lo. mq paag maaib myenb Buaj saa-mu-en, “sau-lo mivb Tauj Kaan-men laavd weig Taaib kanb lyepg nxm Javb hog. Ga'haaq ninb taauj sin Fiag kin-kaan mig a'q.”
15.15: sau-lo tau, “ninb Bua yem aa-maa-lekq myenb uaq txb taaib, weig zu'g pc'g fivj lyrub Fiag kaub lovj Jiaj Eei pa'ki yuvb Zauj vovb weig ziag pun zyruq, meib Eei Tinb huvb. zevg Fiag Eei yetg zuvq yia Bua myetg Revg mig a'q.”
15.13: saa-mu-en Tauj sau-lo uaq zang, sau-lo kxvq Buaj ninb, “Toq zyruq Zeij fu'q pun meib og. yia ei Jyenq zyruq hatg Eei waag zruj zyavj a'q.”
15.1: saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj sau-lo, “zyruq Paaiq yia taaib lovg yrub xn meib zruj huvb kunq ninb Eei pc'g fivj, i-saa-laa-en myenb. weig naaiq ib zang Toq mwavj zyruq Eei waag.
15.26: mq paag saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj sau-lo, “yia maiq Zauj meib Rwrnj, weig zu'g meib kwavg zyruq Eei waag. zyruq Tutq meib Eei huvb weig, pun meib maiq tu'q kunq i-saa-laa-en myenb.”
15.25: ib zang Toq kwavg Gxi yia Eei zwid, yaag Zauj yia Rwrnj weig pun yia zavg zyruq.

13.18: maaib kwanb huvj Jyenq mivb Betg-ho-lon. cvj maaib kwanb huvj Jyenq kapg Jaaij, tovb mavg Fiag sej-Bo-im hxvd Win mivb teib puvb Waav uaq nxm txvj.
13.8: sau-lo yem uaq zuaq siag Nxi, ziuj saa-mu-en tivg Eei zyavb hog, mq paag saa-mu-en maiq kcvb taaib kin-kaan. pc'g fivj zyrug Jiad kxn mivb Raanj a'q.
13.3: yo-naa-Taan Bx'q hivb yem ke-Baa muvq Eei fi-li-saa-tia myenb kruj teib puv pcv Eei zaamg. fi-li-saa-tia myenb yaag hiuq tu'q mig a'q. sau-lo zyrug Paaiq myenb mivb kxmj teib puv pyomq Jxv heug hipq-lu myenb taaib kapq zunq Zwrtq mivb Bx'q Jaaj.”

13.23: fi-li-saa-tia myenb kruj teib puv Eei pcv Zwrtq mivb Tauj Jiaj Bovb Qavj, pia'g mikq-maatq uaq nxm txvj.
13.6: i-saa-laa-en myenb pwatg kanb zu'g sig Niaq haig a'q, pcv yaag zu'g Kruq Jiaj Daavg, pc'g fivj zyrug pyauj mivb pivj Bcvb Kwrtq, Bcvb vaamb, la'pyeib Qavj, Daub Kwrtq Zauj uamb Kwrtq.
13.2: sau-lo yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj kinq pua Zin taub myenb. i Zin taub kan sau-lo yem mikq-maatq Zauj Betg-en Eei Bovb aiq txvj. maaib yetg Zin taub kan yo-naa-Taan yem Ben-yaa-min teig Eei ki-Be-aa zivb. zevg Fiag Eei myenb ninb heug kx'g myenb Rwrnj kx'g myenb Eei pyauq.
13.20: mq paag taub taub i-saa-laa-en myenb xij zu'g mivb fi-li-saa-tia myenb uaq Ryruj ninb Bua Eei laib pyeiq Zauj Pxv Zauj pruq Zauj Ru'g limb.
13.7: maaib teij hipq-lu myenb zuvq pyauj Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib mivb Tauj kaatg Zauj ki-le-aatg teig. sau-lo Zxg yem uaq kin-kaan. yetg zuvq pc'g fivj sin zinj Jyenq kan ninb.
13.19: uaq zang kxmj i-saa-laa-en teib puv lxd maiq tu'q yetg taub Lia'g zavg weig zu'g fi-li-saa-tia myenb kxvq, “Raub heij hipq-lu myenb haib weig kanb taaq Ru'g Daauq taaq Zav.”
13.17: maaib pua kwanb za'g pcv yem fi-li-saa-tia Eei Zyavq Zwrtq taaib. maaib yetg kwanb huvj Jyenq mivb su-an teig Eei o-faa-laa muvq.
13.11: saa-mu-en kxvq, “meib zruj haiq Euvg sig lcb?” sau-lo tau, “yia pwatg pc'g fivj kwavg yia mivb Raanj, meib yaag maiq ziuj meib tivg Eei Nxi taaib. fi-li-saa-tia myenb yaag kapq zunq yem mikq-maatq.
13.5: fi-li-saa-tia myenb kapq zunq xij Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb Bx'q Jaaj. ninb Bua maaib Bx'q Jaaj Eei maab Zia pua waang Jaaj, keb maad pcv Ju'q Zin taub, Zauj yavb Dau Eei pcv Dovg Kxib Len Eei saab zyru Zamq. ninb Bua mivb lyepg Zyavq yem Betg-aa-wen Eei tov puv mcvj, mikq-maatq uaq.
13.9: Navq naaig, sau-lo kxvq, “kunq txb puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq Zauj ziag weig Jiu Tov Eei ka'naaiq taaib yia naaiq.” sau-lo zyrug fovg hxg puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq.
13.16: sau-lo Zauj ninb Eei txn, yo-naa-Taan, Zauj kan ninb Eei myenb yem Ben-yaa-min teig Eei ke-Baa muvq. mq paag fi-li-saa-tia myenb lyepg Zyavq yem mikq-maatq.
13.4: i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb mwavj haid kxvq, “sau-lo Bx'q fi-li-saa-tia myenb kruj teib puv pcv Eei zaamg mig a'q. fi-li-saa-tia myenb yaag za'kevb Rxv haig i-saa-laa-en myenb. sau-lo zyrug heug pc'g fivj taaib Zauj ninb kapq zunq yem kin-kaan.”
13.10: sau-lo Javb Jav fovg hxg puaq ziag liud, saa-mu-en zyrug Tauj taaib a'q. sau-lo Zwrtq mivb zipq, Zauj ninb kxvq wig pwavb waag.
13.22: weig naaiq, Tauj Bx'q Jaaj Eei Nxi, kan sau-lo Zauj yo-naa-Taan Eei myenb maiq maaib yetg taub Eei puad maaib Ru'g Daauq Zauj Zav. Kuvj sau-lo Zauj ninb Eei txn, yo-naa-Taan kanb, maaib Navq.
13.12: yia zyrug kxvq, ‘ib zang fi-li-saa-tia myenb xij taaib kin-kaan Zauj yia Bx'q Jaaj. yia maiq kcvb tu'q Toq zyruq Kxb lyenb.’ yia zyrug haid xij zu'g aapq kanb fovg hxg puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq.”
13.15: saa-mu-en zyrug yem kin-kaan mivb Tauj Ben-yaa-min teig Eei ki-Be-aa zivb. sau-lo saauq kan ninb Eei myenb, maaib leib maiq ko lua'g pc'q taub.
13.13: saa-mu-en kxvq Buaj sau-lo, “meib zruj Vovj Eei sig a'q. meib maiq ei Jyenq zyruq, meib Eei Tinb huvb, Jiu pun meib Eei livg, tovb zyruq hatg zyavj pun meib Eei livg. sij kxvq meib ei nx, ninb zuvq xij pun meib Zauj meib Eei zeib fun yetg liud kunq i-saa-laa-en teib puv.
13.1: sau-lo faauj weig zruj huvb uaq zang ninb Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q faab zyepg Havj. ninb kunq i-saa-laa-en kua'q feij zyepg Eeig Havj.

1.18: han-naa zyrug tau, “Toq meib Kxb lyenb yia, meib Eei msia'q pru.” ninb zyrug mivb mig a'q yaag Eang Naavj. yem naaig taaib ninb Eei Myen maiq Raub a'q.
1.8: han-naa Eei Goj, en-Kaa-naa, naaig ninb, “han-naa aag, meib weig haiq tiug Eyemq, maiq Eang Naavj? meib Eei Hruq weig haiq tiug Raub? maaib yia maiq zeid kaub lovj zyepg taub txn fai?”
1.3: en-Kaa-naa Havb Havj yem ninb Eei pwrnb zivb mivb si-lo paaij yaag fovg hxg ziag pun nrnb Jiaj Eei zyruq. yem uaq maaib e-li Eei i taub txn, hopq-ni Zauj fi-ne-hatg, zruj zyruq Eei sai myenb.
1.21: en-Kaa-naa Zauj ninb Eei yetg pyauq myenb mivb si-lo fovg hxg Havb Havj fovg hxg ziag Eei ka'naaiq pun zyruq yaag mivb Jaauq suv ziuj ninb lcvd Eei vcvg waag.

1.28: weig naaiq yia Zivj taaib txb ninb taaib fuvj pun zyruq. ninb yetg seij penj zyruq Eei mig a'q.” ninb zyrug yem uaq paaij zyruq.
1.7: Havj Jiaj Havj maaib naaiq teij sig Zwrtq. haiq zang han-naa mivb zavg zyruq Eei pyauq, Zauj ninb zruj i Wuab Jeij uaq taub pe-nin-naa zyrug kxvq Zua'q han-naa. han-naa zyrug Eyemq yaag maiq Eang Naavj.
1.19: ta'Eeig Dxm Ryruq Eei ninb Bua Jiad sin taaib paaij liud zyruq zyrug Rwrnj laa-maa zivb, ninb Bua Eei pyauq uaq. en-Kaa-naa Zauj ninb Eei auq pweij, zyruq yaag Javj han-naa tauj kauj Eei waag.
1.17: e-li kxvq, “uaq Euvg, kunq pcvb xn Eei Rwrnj a'q. Toq i-saa-laa-en Eei Tinb huvb ziuj meib tauj kauj Toq Eei waag Zeij pun meib.”
1.27: yia tauj kauj weig xij tu'q naaiq taub fu'Jweiq. zyruq yaag ziuj yia Toq Eei waag Zeij pun yia.
1.11: ninb zyrug lcvd Jiad vcvg waag kxvq, “nrnb Jiaj Eei zyruq aa'b! sij kxvq meib mavg yia, meib Eei msia'q pru Eei naang zivb, yaag Javj yia, maiq la'Ku'q yia, meib Eei msia'q pru nx, meib yaag Zeij taub txn pun yia, meib Eei msia'q pru, yia xij fuvj ninb pun meib weig yetg seij. yia yetg liud yaag maiq Teij ninb Eei mGxvq.”
1.5: mq paag ninb pun i kruq han-naa, weig zu'g ninb Namq haig han-naa. zyruq yaag pun han-naa maiq haib maaib fu'Jweiq.
1.9: ninb Bua yem si-lo Eang liud hopq liud, han-naa zyrug Jiad sin taaib, mivb yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen. uaq zang e-li sai myenb zweid Jyenq zavg zyruq Eei Dopg liub Eei kcvb zrug ka'Len Eei eiq.
1.16: Toq meib maiq tuvq laaig yia, meib Eei msia'q pru, penj maiq zyavb hxvb Eei msia'q txn. tovb yia tauj kauj kxvq uaq teij waag se laaij yia Hruq mun, Hruq Raub Jyenq kxvq.”
1.4: en-Kaa-naa fovg hxg ziag uaq Nxi, ninb zx'q ziag Eei xq taaib pun yetg kruq ninb Eei auq, pe-nin-naa, Zauj pe-nin-naa yuvd Eei txn sia'q fib Navq Eei.
1.10: han-naa Raub tu'q Kruq, Hruq mun haig, Eyemq Jyenq tauj kauj Jrub zyruq.
1.22: mq paag han-naa maiq mivb. ninb kxvq Buaj ninb Eei Goj, “yia maiq kcvb mivb. zuaq Tauj naaiq taub kub vwaad kwavg liud Exj yia Zivj txb ninb mivb Tauj zyruq Eei Ra'Myen yaag pun ninb yetg liud yem uaq.”

1.13: han-naa Kuvj yem Hruq tauj kauj, Rwib meij Eapq Eapq teij Navq. mwavj maiq haid ninb Eei Qiaj. e-li zyrug laaig han-naa tiuq Gwin mig a'q.
1.1: yem e-faa-im Bovb aiq txvj Eei laa-maa-Taa-im muvq, maaib taub e-faa-im myenb, Buaj heug en-Kaa-naa. ninb zruj ye-lo-ham Eei txn, e-li-hu Eei fun, To-hu Eei fa'q. To-hu zruj supg Eei txn.

1.25: ninb Bua taij uaq taub vovb kruq yaag txb uaq taub fu'Jweiq Tauj e-li uaq.

26.8: aa-Bi-Qai kxvq Buaj Daa-witq, “ib Nxi Tinb huvb zx'q meib Eei winb wavq Jiu pun yem meib Eei puad mig a'q. ib zang Toq meib pun yia lovg Zav Ropq ninb pavg ka'Diaq Dau tiv Jyenq maa'b! Ropq yetg Rung Navq, maiq zu'g Ropq ta'Eeig Rung.”

26.21: sau-lo kxvq, “yia zruj txvg a'q. yia Eei txn, Daa-witq aa'b! kunq Rwrnj taaib weig zu'g ib Nxi meib funj yia Eei mcvg Jaaij. yem naaiq mivb yia maiq cvj Jiad Hruq hxig meib a'q. yia zruj Vovj Eei Jauq yaag zruj txvg Lo haig.”
26.14: Daa-witq zyrug naug Jyenq heug uaq teij Junb pcv Zauj ne Eei txn, apg-ne, “apg-ne aa'b! meib maiq tau fai?” apg-ne tau, “meib se haiq taub kaamq heug huvb tiaj?”
26.23: zyruq Zeij zivb Eeig pun taub taub myenb ziuj ninb Bua zruj tu'q hxpg yaag zyepg zua'q Eei zruj. weig zu'g ib Nxi zyruq zx'q meib Jiu pun yem yia Eei puab Diaq. yia maiq Fiag puad hxig zyruq lovg yrub xn taaib Eei myenb.
26.6: Daa-witq naaig hitq-Tai myenb, aa-hi-me-lekq, Zauj sej-lu-yaa Eei txn, yo-aapg Eei yrud, aa-Bi-Qai, “haiq taub xij Zauj yia mivb sau-lo Eei Zyavq?” aa-Bi-Qai tau, “yia Zauj meib mivb.”
26.2: sau-lo zyrug txb Jyenq ninb kinq taaib Eei pua Zin taub i-saa-laa-en pcv, Fiag sipg-aa teib puvb Waav mivb lxd Daa-witq.
26.20: weig naaiq, ib zang maiq tuvq pun yia leib zyruq ko, zu'g Ryaamq lyrug Fiag Dau, weig zu'g i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb Zwrtq taaib xij zx'q yia Eei mcvg, Navq yetg taub myenb yem Bov zung nxm nx'g Jiab nx.”
26.24: ib Nxi yia pwatg huvb tiaj Eei mcvg Jaaij. Toq zyruq yaag pwatg yia Eei mcvg Jaaij yaag Fruj yia pyauj Dutq yetg zuvq Kruq naang Eei Jauq.”
26.7: Daa-witq Zauj aa-Bi-Qai luvb mwrnd zang Fiag mivb Tauj sau-lo Eei Zyavq, pwatg sau-lo pweij Jyenq Zyavq Bu'Dovj mFxmb. ninb Eei Zav Ropq Jyenq Dau nitq ninb Eei mGxvq. apg-ne Zauj zwavj pcv pweij Wiv kxmj huvb tiaj.
26.19: ib zang Toq yia Eei zyruq, huvb tiaj, mwavj meib Eei pru Eei waag. sij kxvq zyruq Zo'q meib zruj pun yia nx, Toq zyruq zipq fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq. mq paag sij kxvq myenb Zo'q meib nx, Toq pun ninb Bua yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen zu'g zyruj. weig zu'g ib Nxi ninb Bua zung yia Zwrtq mivb, maiq pun yia Ripg zyruq Zeij pun yia Ripg Eei pwrng. ninb Bua kxvq, ‘mivb a'q. mivb fub suj Eiag Eei zyenb maa'b!’
26.17: sau-lo zia'q tu'q Daa-witq Eei Qiaj zyrug kxvq, “yia Eei txn, Daa-witq aa'b! naaiq meib Eei Qiaj fai?” Daa-witq tau, “huvb tiaj aa'b! zeid Eei. yia Eei Qiaj.”
